\id JOS  
\h Joshua 
\toc1 Joshua Lekhabu 
\toc2 Joshua 
\toc3 Joshua 
\mt1 JOSHUA  
\mt2 LEKHABU  
\mt3 Joshua Lekhabu Sung Thu Umdan  
\ip Nathil gon losamna um kha em? Israel te ana losam uve… Tahsan lhahsamna le thungai louna jeh in kum somthum le get jen athil gon-u lolhingjou louvin ana tang un ahi. Hiche jouchun phat kilemchang khat ahung um'in, hichu alhaso tapouve! Thungai toh thon ache tauvin ahileh, galmite ajou un, phat sottah ananga jing’u alungtup uchu Molson aum tan ahi.  
\ip Joshua lekhabu hi hopnin akihom khen in, amasapa hin hansanna, tahsan, thil kidangtahtah chule galmite jona thudol aseijin ahi. Lungtup ahilouleh thilgon khat molso kiti hi boltheina jeh ahipon, let le neo jong ahipon chule nei le gou jeh jong ahipoi. Amavang Pathen tahsan le Ama thungaija bou kingam ahi!  
\ip Joshua lekhabu hop nina chan hin Pathen tohgon akijom peh in—Itobang gim le hesoh dinmun hijongleh Pathen'in amite adalha ngaipon, ama ama nam sunga chamna le thudih’a akhosah nadiuvin gam le go kicheh tah apen ahi. Hiche lekhabu nasim’a kon hi Pathen'in nam som le ni ho chunga kicheh tah thilgon anei nasimdoh ding kitil khouna’a nanei thei ding ahi. Hichebang chun Pathen'in mimal cheh chunga thilgon aneiye ti, akicheh in ahi.  
\is1 Lekhabu Jihpa Chule Ajih Kum  
\ip Lekhabu hi Johsua in anajih ahi. Chule achaina lam Joushua thi-opna thudol hi Aaron chapa Eleazar thempu in ajih ahi. Hichu 1390 BC vel’a kijih ahi.  
\c 1  
\s1 Pathen In Joshua Atilkhou  
\p
\v 1 Pakai lhacha Mose athiphatnin Nun chapa Mose lhacha a pang Joshua kom'a chun Pakaiyin thu ahin seijin,  
\v 2 “Kalhacha Mose athitai, hijeh chun nangma kipatnin lang hiche Jordan hi galkaijin, nang le hiche mipi ho hin Keiman Israel chate kapehna gam hi jonlut tauvin.  
\v 3 Mose kom'a kanateppehna bang banga chu hoilai mun hijongleh nakengphang’un achotphana muntin chu nangho kapehding nahiuve. \x + \xo 1:3 \xt Danbu Ni Na 11:24,25\x*  
\v 4 Gamthip gam le Lebanon gam'a vadunglen changgei, Eupharates vadung, Hit mite gampumpi chuleh nisa lhumna lang twikhanglen changgei nagam’u hi ding ahi.  
\v 5 Nahinkho lhumkeijuva namasang uva koimacha dingjoulou ding, Mose kana dinpi banga nangho jong kadinpi jingdiu, kadalhah louheldiu chuleh kanungsun louhel ding nahiuve. \x + \xo 1:5 \xt Danbu Ni Na 31:6,8; Heb 13:5\x*  
\v 6 Hatninlang hangin, hiche mite hi pehdinga apu apateu kanateppeh gamchu agoulo diuva nahoppeh ding ahi. \x + \xo 1:6 \xt Danbu Ni Na 31:6,7,23\x*  
\v 7 Hatninlang hangpou pouvin, Kalhacha Mose kanapeh danthu jouse nanit jouna dingin, hichea konhin jetlang hihen veiling hijongleh kiheimang hihbeh’in, chutileh nachena channa nakhantou theiding ahi.  
\v 8 Hiche danthubu hi, nakamma kon mangthah louhel ding, amavang asun ajanna nageljoh ding, akijih dungjuiya hi nachon jingdiu ahi. Chitilebou nakhantou ding chuleh nalolhin tei ding'u ahi.  
\v 9 Keiman thupeh kahinpeh louva nabol ham? Hatninlang hangin, kicha hihbeh’in, tijatna jong neihih in ajeh chu na Pakai na Pathen'in nachena chan’uva nalhonpi jing dingu ahi,” ati.   
\s1 Joshua’n Israel te Atohdiu Aseipeh  
\p
\v 10 Chujou chun, Josuha’in mipi lamkaiho chu thu apen hitin aseije,  
\v 11 “Ponbuh sunga khun cheuvin lang mipi ho khu anehdiu akigot toh dingun gaseipeh’un, ajeh chu nithum sunga hi Jordan luipi khu nagalkaijuva Pakai na Pathen'in napeh’u gamkhu galotauvin.  
\v 12 Chuleh Reuben phungleh Gad phung chuleh Mannasseh phung akehkhat ho kom'a chun Joshua’n hitin aseije, \x + \xo 1:12 \xt Minbu 32:28-32; Danbu Ni Na 3:18-20; Joshua 22:1-6\x*  
\v 13 Pakai lhacha Mose’n nakom uva aseichu sumil hih’un, Pakai na Pathen'un nakicholdosah tauvin, chuleh hiche gamhi napeh’u ahitai.  
\v 14 Najiteule nachateu, chuleh naganchateu chu Mose’n napehnao hiche Jordan solam gamkaiyah hin umsah’un, ahinlah nalah’uva gal-hat ho leh mihangsan chengse chun galmanchah akipat uva asopihou masanga hi gal lamkaija pangdiu,  
\v 15 Pakaiyin nangho gam napeh bang uva amaho jong alodiu gam apeh kahseuva nakithopidiu ahi. Chujou tengleh nahung kileuva Pakai lhacha Mose’n napehnao Jordan solam nagam uva nachendiu ahi.  
\v 16 Hiti chun ama hon Joshua chu adonbutnun, “Ipi hileh nangin neithupeh jouseu chu kaboldiu, chuleh neisol solnauva chu kache jengdiu ahi atiuve”.  
\v 17 “Keihon Mose thu kanangai bang bang uva chu imalam jousea nangma thu jong kangai diu ahi. Pakai na Pathen chun Mose ana umpi bang bangin nangjong naumpi jinghen,” atiuve.  
\v 18 “Koi hileh nangma thupeh jouse chu nitlouva aumma, nahindouva aumpoupou leh thadoh jengding ahi. Hatninlang hangpou pouvin”.   
\c 2  
\s1 Rahab In Gamvelhi’a Cheho Ahuhdoh  
\p
\v 1 Nun chapa Joshua’n Shittim’a kon'in aguh’a gamvelhi dingin mini anasoldoh’in hiti hin anavailhah’in ahi. Chelhonnin lang Jericho geijin agamchu gakholpeh lhonnin ati. Hiti chun amani achelhonnin Rahab notinu in na agalhung lhonnin hicheachun agageh lhontan ahi. \x + \xo 2:1 \xt Heb 11:31; Jac 2:25\x*  
\v 2 Hiche chu Jericho lengpa kom agalhut tauvin, “Ven, hiche gam kholtoh dingin Israel mi phabep tujannin ahung uve,” agatiuvin ahi.  
\v 3 Hichun Jericho lengpan Rahab kom'a chun mi asollin hiti hin agaseisah e, “Hiche gamsung velhi dinga hungho nainna hunglut ho chu hinpuidoh’in” atin ahi.  
\v 4 Rahab chun miteni chu anasel ahinai, ahinla aman anadonbutnin, “Amani chu ahunglhkonnai ahin hoiya konna hunglhonham ti keiman kahepoi.  
\v 5 Kho ahung jinkon kelkot kikhading konchakhun apotdoh lhontai, hoilangpen ajotlhon ham keiman kahepoi, delloi leuchun naphahdiu ahi,” ati.  
\v 6 Ahinlah amanun amani chu indan chunglanga apuitouvin patkung lom inchunga anaphou lah a chun asellin ahi.  
\v 7 Hiche jouchun lengpa sepaiten Jordan panmun lampi geijin aganungdel’un ahi. Anungdel ho chu apotdoh jou jouvun Jericho khopi kelkot chu akhahtauvin ahi.  
\v 8 Gamvelhi teni jan alup masang lhonin, Rahab inchunga amani chu kihoulimpi dingin kaltouvin,  
\v 9 ajah lhkonnah hitin aseije, “Pakaiyin hiche gamhi nangho napeh’u ahitai ti keiman kahei, nangho ginnan eilodim tauvin, hiche gam mitehi nangho kichatna a tijagam kahi tauve.  
\v 10 Ajeh chu Egypt gam'a konna nahung potdoh’u chun Pakaiyin nangho dingin Twipi San Achansah’in, chuleh Jordan luigal langa um Amor lengteni Sihor le Og na suhmang hellu jongchu kana jauvin ahi. \x + \xo 2:10 \xt Potdohbu 14:21; \xt Minbu 21:21-35\x*  
\v 11 Hiche thu hi kajah jeh’un kalunguhi alhalhop jengin, nangho kimaitopi ding hi koima angapcha umtalou ahi. Ajeh chu Pakai na Pathen'u hi thaneitah, chunga van le noiya lei Pathen ahi.  
\v 12 Hijeh chun, keiman nangni kakithopi lhon bang’a hi nangnin jong kei le ka insung mite hi kh otona nei neilhonding hinam Pakai minin kihahsellhon’inlang,  
\v 13 Hiche Jericho khopi hi nalah tengu leh, kapa le kanu, kasopi pasal ho le kasopi numeiho, ka insung mite jouseule keima neihinghoi diu hinam amelchihna khat neipelhonin ati.  
\v 14 Amanin adonbut lhonnin, nangin neiseidoh lhonlou pouleh na insungu hoidohna dingin keini hinkho hi kakitepnalhon ahiyenge. Pakaiyin hiche gamhi eipeh tengu leh kakitepna lhon dungjuiya khotona kahin neidiu ahi atilhonne.  
\v 15 Hichejou chun, Rahab in jong, amanichu khaokhat nin bangkotna konchun agahkhailhan ahi. Ajeh chu Rahab inchu hiche khopi kulpi pala kingam'a ahi.  
\v 16 Amanun ajahlhkonnah, “Molchung langa kaltou lhonnin, ajole minungdel ho chun nahin tohkha get unte, hicheachun nithum hung umlhonnin minungdel ho chu ahung kile kahsen kisel lhonnin, chujou tengleh nachenanom lhkonnah chetheilhon tan,” ati.  
\v 17 Apotdoh masang lhonnin, amanin amanu kom'a chun, “Nanghon nakiseipeh’u dungjuiya hi nahung chonnuleh keiho jong kakitepnao bangahi kahintohdiu ahi atilhonne.  
\v 18 Keiho hi hiche gam'ahi kahung tengu leh nangin hiche khaosan hi keini neikhailhah lhkonna hiche bangkotna konna hi nana khailhahding ahi. Chujou teng, na insung mite jouse, napa, nang, nasopiho jousele na insung mite jouse na insung uva hi nana umdiu ahi.  
\v 19 Ijemtia napotdoh’uva lamlen dunga nana chekhah uva nathikhah uva ahileh keiho thepmo hilou ding ahi. Amavang hiche insunga hi naummuva khat touvin nasuhkhah uleh hitobanga thina nato-uleh keiho mopohna hi ding ahi.  
\v 20 Ahinlah nang hon neijoulhep uva ahivang leh hiche kihahsel nahi panna bei hi ding ahi,” ati peh lhonne.  
\v 21 Amanun “Nasei lhonchu kapomme,” ati. Hiti chun amani chu asoldoh’in, khaosan chu bangkotna chun akhaitan ahi.  
\v 22 Gamvelhi tenichu thinglhang gam langah akaltou lhonnin nithum agachaam lhonnin ahi. Amani nungdel ho chun lamlen langchu muntin aga phetleng jengun ahinlah ajona’in lolhing louvin ahung kiletauvin ahi.  
\v 23 Hichun gamvelhi tenichu thinglhang gam'a kon'in ahung kumsuh lhonnin Jordan vadung ahinpal galkai lhonnin Joshua kom'a chun thilsoh jouse chu alhut lhontan ahi.  
\v 24 Pakaiyin gamjouse hi eipe tauve, ajeh chu agammite ho jouse khu eiho kichatnan atija-gam tauve atilhonne.   
\c 3  
\s1 Israel te Jordan Agalkai-U  
\p
\v 1 Joshua chu Israel te jouse toh jingpitah in Shittim ahindalhauvin Jordan vadung pang chu ahunglhungun, galkaipai louvin hilai munna chun ngahmun akisem tauvin ahi.  
\v 2 Hiti chun nithum jouvin Israel lamkaiho chu ngahmunna chun acheuvin, mipi ho chu thupeh aganeijun,  
\v 3 Mipiho chu thupeh aganeijun, “Nanghon Pakai na Pathen'u kitepna thingkong khu Levi thempuhon ahinputnu namu tengu leh naumnao muncheh’uva kon'in kipatnunlang anungu juiyin atiuve.  
\v 4 Nangho hiche lampia hi nana chekhah loujeh’un ama hon napuidiu ahi. Nangho le amaho kikahchu tong sangni hi ding hiche kalvalla hi nachenai louheldiu ahi,” atiuve.  
\v 5 Hichun Joshua’n mipi ho kom'a chun nangho le nangho kisuthengun, ajeh chu jing nikho leh Pakaiyin nangho lah a thil kidang abol ding ahi ati.  
\v 6 Chuleh Joshua thempuho kom'a chun aseijin, “Kitepna thingkong chu pu-uvin lang mipi ho masang langa chun cheuvin,” ati. Hichun amaho akipatdoh’un, kitepna thingkong chu apu-uvin mipi ho masanga chun acheuvin ahi.  
\v 7 Pakaiyin Joshua kom'a chun, “Tuni hin keiman nangmahi Israel mite jousea mitmua katunlet ding nahi, chutengleh ama hon Mose kana umpi bang banga nangjong kaumpi inghy ahetdoh theidiu ahi.  
\v 8 Kitepna thingkongpua thempuho kom'a chun hiche thupeh hi seipeh’in, nangho Jordan vadung pang nalhun tengu leh Jordan vadung chu gahchonlutnun lang ding dennun,” ati.  
\v 9 Hiti chun Joshua’n jong Israel te jah a chun “Hungun lang Pakai na Pathen'un ipi najahsah nommuvem hung ngaijun,  
\v 10 Tunia hi nang hon hingjing Pathen chu nalah’uva aumme ti nahetdiu ahi. Aman Caanan mite, Hit mite, Hivi mite, Periz mite, Girgas mite, Amor mite chule Jebus mite jouse namasanguva nanomang pehdiu ahi.  
\v 11 Ven, vannoi leiset pumpi Pakai kitepna thingkong chun nangho hiche Jordan vadunga hi napuigalkai diu ahi.  
\v 12 Tun, Israel phung som le ni lah a konchun, phungkhatna mikhat lhengdoh’inlang,  
\v 13 Vannoi leiset pumpi Pakai thingkong chu thempuhon aputdiu, akengun twi agah chotkhah khah leh sahlanga konna twi hunglonglha chu tanjengding, chuleh vadung chu banglai banga kikhang jengding ahi,” ati.  
\v 14 Hiti chun mipi ho chun angahmunnu chu ahin dalhauvin Jordan palgalkai dingchun ahung kijottauve, chuleh kitepna thingkongpua thempu ho chu ahung masauvin ahi.  
\v 15 Hichu chang at phatlai ahijeh’in Jordan chu akamma twi letjenga ahi. Ahinla thingkongpua thempuho kengchun vadung geichin twilah chu agah chotkhah phatnun,  
\v 16 Sahlanga konna hunglonglha twichu akitintang jengin Adam kiti Zerethen kom'a khopi geichun gamla tah geijin twi alom changing akikhanghel jengin ahi. Chuleh hiche noilanga twi ho chu alon kanghel tokah’in Dead Sea ah alonglutnin ahi. Hijeh chun mipi ho chu Jericho khopi kom'a chun agalkaijun ahi.  
\v 17 Hiti chun mipi ho akijot sungu chun Pakai thingkongpu thempuho chu vadungkim tolgolai jachun ading dennun ahi. Ama hon Israel nampumpi chu Jordan tolgolai ajot galkaisoh tokah’in angah’un ahi.   
\c 4  
\s1 Melchihna Song Kiphut  
\p
\v 1 Mipiho chu Jordan agalkai sohhel phatnun, Pakaiyin Joshua kom'a chun thu ahinseije,  
\v 2 “Tun phungtinna kon'in pasal som le ni lhengdoh’inlang,  
\v 3 Jordan vadung lailung nadinnauva kon'in song som le ni hinchoidoh’un, hichu choijunlang tunilhah’a nagenadiu munnachun sekhommun,” ati.  
\v 4 Hiti chun Joshua’n Israel phungtinna konna alhendoh som le ni ho chu akoukhom’in,  
\v 5 Amaho kom'a chun, “Jordan lailung Pakai na Pathen'u thingkong masanga khun cheuvinlang mikhatnin songkhat cheh na lengkou uvah hinpuuvin lang, Israel phung som le ni a kon'in phungkhat’a songkhat cheh, song som le ni chu hinchoijun tin aseipeh’in ahi.  
\v 6 Eihon hiche song ho hi melchihna khatna imandiu ahi. Khonungtengleh nachateuvin hiche songhi ipi vetsahna ham tia ahindoh tengu leh,  
\v 7 Nanghon hitia hi nadonbutdiu ahi, Pakai kitepna thingkong chu akiput galkai phat chun Jordan vadung chu atanghel jengtan ahi, Israel mipiten itihchan hijongleh ahetjingna diuva hiche songho hi amelchihna hi ding ahi tia naseipehdiu ahi.” ati.  
\v 8 Hiti chun mipi hon Joshua athupeh bang bangin abol’un ahi. Pakaiyin Joshua ana thupeh bang bangin Jordan vadung lailunga konchun phung khatna songkhat chehtoh kitoh dingin song chu som le ni ahin puuvin ahi. Ama hon hichu ajangenau ngahmunnah apolutnun het jingna song dingin aphut tauvin ahi.  
\v 9 Joshua’n jong achombeh’in Jordan lailunga kitepna thingkong puho keng phangin achotphanau laitah’a chun song som le ni aphutnin ahi. Hichechu tuni geijin aumnalaijin ahi.  
\v 10 Mose’n Pakai thupeh ho Joshua anapehson ho chu akitoldoh sohkei tokah’in thingkongpua thempuho chu vadung lailunga chun dding jingun ahi. Alangkhatnah mipi ho chu kinotah in vadung chu agalkaijun ahi.  
\v 11 Mipiho jouse chu bitkeija agalkai sohkei phatnun Pakai thingkong puho jongchu mipi ho mitmu changtah chun agalkaijun ahi.  
\v 12 Galmanchah kichoi Reuben leh Gad phungmi ho leh Manasseh phung akehkhatnin Mose thupeh bangin Israel te chu alamkaijun Jordan agalkai masauvin ahi.  
\v 13 Hitobanga galmanchah kichoi mihem sangsomli ho chu galsat dinga kigosadem ahiuve, chuleh, amaho chu Pakai mapuina changpummin Jericho khopi phaicham lang’ah chun agalkai tauvin ahi.  
\v 14 Hiche nikho chun Pakaiyin Joshua chu Israel te jouse mitmun atunglennin ahi, hiti chun ama hon ahinkho lhumkeijin agingun, Mose anaja bang bangun jana anapeuvin ahi.  
\v 15 Pakaiyin Joshua kom'a chun hitin anaseije,  
\v 16 “Vadung tolhgo laiya konchun Pakai kitepna thingkongpu ho chu hungdoh dingin thu pen,” ati.  
\v 17 Hiti chun Joshua’n jong thupeh chu agah neitan ahi.  
\v 18 Pakai kitepna thingkongpu thempuho chu vadung golaija konna ahungpotdoh uva akengphangun vadung pang tolgo lah chu ahinchot phat’uvin Jordan vadung twichu ahunglong kitnin tumasanga bang bangin vadung pang aletdoh sohkei kittan ahi.  
\v 19 Mipichun lhamasa nisom channi chun Jordan chu ahung galkaijun Jericho solam Gilgal munna chun ngahmun asemmun ahi.  
\v 20 Joshua’n Jordan vadunga konna song som le ni ahinlah chu hiche Gilgal munnahin alomchang’in asekhommin ahi.  
\v 21 Hichun Joshua’n Israel te kom'a chun aseijin, “Khonungleh nachateuvin hiche hi ipi vetsahna ham tia nahindoh tengu leh,  
\v 22 Hiteng chuleh nang hon hiche laiya hi Israel chaten Jordan tolgo laiya ahung galkaina munnu chu ahi tia nadonbutdiu ahi,  
\v 23 Ajeh chu, na Pakai na Pathen'un nangho mitmu tah’a twichu Achansah’a hitia chu twikhanglensan igalkaisoh kahseuva Achansah banga chu igalkai sohkei tokah uva akansah ahin,  
\v 24 Leiset chunga nam jousen Pakai banthahat anatatje ahetsohna diuleh nang hon jong Pakai na Pathen'u itihchan hijongleh naginjing theina diu ahi tia naseipehdiu ahi.” tin aseipeh tai.   
\c 5  
\p
\v 1 Jordan lhumlamma cheng Amor mite lengho leh Mediterranean panga cheng Canaan mite lenghon Israel mipitehi a Pathen'un Jordan vadung asuhkhangpeh’in ahin palgalkai sahtai ti ajahdoh phatnun kichatnan alungthimmu alhulhop gamtauvin ahi.   
\s1 Gilgal Munna Chep Kitan  
\p
\v 2 Hiche pettah chu Pakaiyin Joshua kom'a h “Songhem chu chemcha bangin semminlang Israel te chu akhangni channin achep’u tanpeh’in,” ati.  
\v 3 Hiti chun Joshua’n jong songhem chemchan asemmin Israel te chu Gibeath-haaraoth munnah achep’u anatanpeh’in ahi.  
\v 4 Joshua’n amaho chu achepmu atanpeh louva khoh-a ahi, ajeh chu Egypt ahin dalhah uva galsatthei pasal ho jouse chu gamthip gam'a anathigam ah ahi tauve. \x + \xo 5:4 \xt Minbu 14:28-35\x*  
\v 5 Egypt hindalha a pasal ho jouse chu achepmu anakitan sohkeija ahiuvin, Ahinlah Egypt ma konna ahungpotdoh uva gamthip noija ahung kholjinnao kumsunga pengho chu achepmu kitan loulai ngen ahiuve.  
\v 6 Israel ten Egypt ahin dalhah uva galsatthei jouse athigam kahseuva kum somli sunghi gamthip noija hung kholjinna ahiuve. Ajeh chu ama hon Pakai thupeh anitlou jeh’un Pakaiyin khoiju le bongnoi lonna gam pehdinga ateppehnao gamchu alutsahlouna dinga ana kihahsella ahi.  
\v 7 Hijeh chun Joshua’n apateu mun lothei dinga hung kikhanlhit ho chu achepmu atanpeh’u ahi. Ajeh chu amaho hin gamtepgam ahinjotnauva hi achepmu ana kitan khaloulai ngen ahiuve.  
\v 8 Pasal jouse achepmu akitan jehchun amaho adamdoh kahsen ngahmunna chun ana kicholdou tauvin ahi.  
\v 9 Hichun Pakaiyin Joshua kom'a chun “Tunia hi Egypt gam'a nasohchan nauva najumnao chu katolmangpeh’u ahitai,” ati. Hijeh a chu hiche mun chu tunichan geija Gilgal kitia ahitai.  
\v 10 Israel ten Gilgal munna ngahmun asemsungu lhamasa nisomle nili chan nilhahchun Jericho phaichamma Kalchuh Kut anamangun ahi. \x + \xo 5:10 \xt Potdohbu 12:1-13\x*  
\v 11 Hichejou ajing nikhotah chun agamsungsoh agamga cholsolou changlhah a kisemleh anchang kikang chu anapantauvin ahi.  
\v 12 ama hon agamsungsoh agamga aneh masat ni uva pat chun Manna akimutapon, mujong akimukit mongmong tapon ahi. \x + \xo 5:12 \xt Potdohbu 16:35\x*   
\s1 Pakai Sepai Jalamkaipan Joshua Akimaitopi  
\p
\v 13 Joshua chu Jericho khopi kom agalhun chun akhodah in chunglang agahvetleh akhutna chemjam kichoi mikhat amasanga adinchu amun ahi. Joshua chun ajonlutnin amapa chu ana dongin, “Nanghi eipanpi ding kagol nahim ahilouleh galmi nahim? ati.  
\v 14 Ama chun ahindonbutnin “Khatchachu kahipoi, keima Pakai sepaite lamkaija pang tua hi hungkon kahitai,” ati. Hichun Joshua chu tolla abohkhupmin achibeijin, “Ka Pakaiyin nalhacha keima hi ipi neibolsah got ham?” ati.  
\v 15 Pakai sepaite lamkai pa chun adonbutnin, “Nakengkoh chu sutlhan ajeh chu nadinna chu muntheng ahi,” ati. Hichun Joshua’n aseibang chun aboltai.   
\c 6  
\s1 Jericho Khopi Kisuhchim  
\p
\v 1 Tun Jericho mipite chun Israel te chu akichat jeh’un akhopiu kelkot chu akam chahkheh jengun ahi. Mi koimacha avadohsah pouvin lutjong alutsah pouvin ahi.  
\v 2 Ahinlah Pakaiyin Joshua kom'a h, “Hiche khopi leh alengpau chuleh asepaiteu jouse jong nakhutna kapehdoh ahitai.  
\v 3 Nangleh nasepai chengsetoh nigup sunga hi nisehleh khopihi khatvei naveldiu ahi.  
\v 4 Thingkong masanga hi thempu sagi in kelchalki khat cheh akichoijuva kijotdiu ahi. Nisagi channileh nang hon hiche khopihi sagivei naveldiu ahi.  
\v 5 Thempuhon kelchalki ho chu ahinmut mutnuleh mipiten na-o neichasun sunnuva sangtah a nasapdiu ahi. Hiteng chuleh khopi kulpi chu chimlhading, hiteng chuleh mipi ho chu khopi sunga chu nalhailutnuva nadelkhum jengdiu ahi,” ati.  
\v 6 Hiti chun Joshua in thempuho chu akoukhommin hiti hin aseipeh tai, “Pakai kitepna thingkong chu puuvinlang, thempu sagi chun kelchalki kichoi cheh’unlang mipi masanga khun kijotnun” ati.  
\v 7 Hijouchun aman mipi ho chu thu apen, “Khopi vella chun kijotnun, galmanchah kichoi chengse chu Pakai thingkong masanga cheuhenlang mipi chu lamkai juhen,” ati.  
\v 8 Joshua’n mipi ho kom'a thu anaseijouchun Thempu sagiho chun pengkul akichoi cheh’un Pakai masanga chun akijotnun pengkul ho chu amutnun ahi. Chuleh Pakai kitepna thingkong chu ajuijun ahi.  
\v 9 Galmanchah kichoi phabep chu pengkul kichoi thempuho masanga akijotnun, loikhatchu thingkong nunglanga akijotnun, thempuho chun pengkul chu amutjom jingun ahi.  
\v 10 Joshua’n thu ahinpen, “Koimachan kholhang samhih’un, paojong paopoh hih’un, keiman sammun kati tokah’in thu chengkhatcha jong nakammuva kon'in gindohsah hih’un,” ati.  
\v 11 Hiti chun Pakai thingkong chu apuuvin hiche nikho chun khatvei khopi chu avellun, chujouvin abonchauvin ngahmun chu ajonnun agageh’un ahi.  
\v 12 Ajingin Joshua chu jingkah matah in akipatdoh’in ahileh thempuho jongchun Pakai thingkong chu apukitnun ahi.  
\v 13 Thempu sagi ho chun pengkul chu akichoi cheh’un Pakai thingkong masanga chun akijotnun, pengkul chu amutnun ahi. Avellin, galmanchah kichoi ho chu pengkul kichoi thempu ho masangleh Pakai thingkong puho nung’ah akijotnun ahi. Hiche sungse hin thempuho chun pengkul chu amut mutjingun ahi.  
\v 14 Anini channa’in jong ama hon khopi chu avelkitnun chujouvin ngahmunna ahung kile kitnun ahi. Hitobang hin nigup sungse chun abollun ahi.  
\v 15 Nisagi channa’in Israel te chu khovahlhah’in akipatdoh’un tumasanga abol bang bangun khopi chu avel kitnun ahi. Ahin tuchung ahin khopi chu sagivei avellun ahi.  
\v 16 Sagivei aveljouvun thempuhon pengkul thongjen junnin ahin mutphat uchun Joshua’n mipi ho chu thu ahinpen, “Kholhang sammun! Pakaiyin hiche khopi hi nepeh’u ahitai!  
\v 17 Jericho khopi leh asunga um jouse hi Pakaiyin asuhmang sohkei ding ahitai: Rahab kijohnu leh a insung mite jouse chu kihing hoiding ahi, ajeh chu amanun gamvelhi’a kibol ho chu ana hoidoh sah’in ahi.  
\v 18 Suhmang dinga um thilho chu khatcha suloh hihbeh’un, achutilouleh nangho jong nakisuhmang tha dingu ahi, chuleh Israel ngahmunna hi hamsetna nahin lhutkhumlo diu ahi.  
\v 19 Amavang dangka le sana, chule thih le sum-eng’a kisem thilho chu Pakaiya atheng ahin hiche ho chu Pakai sumkholna a lutding ahi,” tin thupeh ana neitai.  
\v 20 Mipiho chun pengkul kimutgin chu ajahphatnun a-ou neichasunnun asammun ahileh Jericho kulpi chu achimlha jengin ahi. Hiche phat chun Israel ten khopi sungchu anokhummun alatauve. \x + \xo 6:20 \xt Heb 11:30\x*  
\v 21 ama hon khopi sunga umho jouse, numei pasal, ateh akhang, bong, kelngoi, kelcha chuleh sangan abonchan asumang sohkeijun ahi.  
\v 22 Hichun Joshua’n gamvelhia cheteni kom'a chun, nakitepna lhon dungjuijin akijohnu innachun lutlhonnin lang amanu le a insung mite jouse chu gapuidoh lhonnin ati.  
\v 23 Gamvelhia cheteni chu achelut lhonnin Rahab chu ama toh umkhom apale anu, asopiho le aisungmite jouse chutoh agapuidoh lhonnin ahi.  
\v 24 Hijouchun, Israel ten khopi chu asunga um jouse toh ahallhauvin asumanghel tauvin ahi. Ahin sumle sana, chule sum-eng le thih-a kisem thilho vang chu Pakai sumkholna munnah akoijun ahi.  
\v 25 Hiti chun Joshua’n Rahab kijohnu chu insunga aumkhopi a insung mite jouse toh ahuhdoh’in ahi, ajeh chu aman Jericho velhi dinga asolteni chu anaseldoh’a ana hoidohsah lhon ahi. \x + \xo 6:25 \xt Heb 11:31\x*  
\v 26 Hichun, Joshua’n Jericho khopi chu anagaosap’in, “Koi hileh hiche Jericho khopi sapha go chanchu Pakai sapset changhen, tungdohgoa chu acha masapen’in loulo hen, akelkot tungdohgoa chu achapa lhumpen chaanlo hen,” ati. \x + \xo 6:26 \xt 1 Lgt 16:34\x*  
\v 27 Hiti chun Pakaiyin Joshua chu anaumpin hijeh chun gamsung pumpia chun amin ana kithanglheh jeng tan ahi.   
\c 7  
\s1 Israel ten Ai Khopi Alel’u  
\p
\v 1 Ahinla Israel’in sapset changsa thilho chungahin thupeh anapalkeh’un ahi. Achan kitipa hin sapset changsa thilho phabep chu ana gudohtan, hijeh chun Pakai chu Israel chungah analunghang lheh jengin ahi. Achan kitipa hi, Judaphung sunga Zerah chapa Zimri chilhah’a kon Carmi chapa ahi.  
\v 2 Joshua’n Jericho a kon'in, Beth’aven kom, Bethel solama um Ai khopi velhi dingin mi phabep asollin ahi.  
\v 3 Amaho ahung kile phatnun Joshua kom'a chun hitin aseijun ahi, “Eiho ibonnuva ichetouvu angaipoi ajeh chu hiche Ai khopi nokhum ding khun mi sangni ahilouleh sangthum kal ngaiponte atiuvin ahi. Amahokhu lhomchabou ahiuvin eiho iboncha uva ichetoukhoh’u angaipoi atiuve.”  
\v 4 Hijeh chun mi sangthum tobang asollun ahileh gimneitah in gal ahinlal tauvin ahi.  
\v 5 Ai khomiten Israel ho chu akhopiu kelkotna kon'in Sheberim geijin ahin dellutnun lamsah lamma nungjam ho chu mi somthum le gup tobang athatnun ahi. Hitobang thilsoh’a konhin Israel te chu kichatnan adimtauvin alungu adailheh jengtauvin ahi.  
\v 6 Joshua leh Israel upate jouse lunghemmin aponsillu abot-eh jengun, aluchanguvah leivui akinu’vin Pakai thingkong maija chun tolla abohkhup un nilhahlang geijin akisehgim jengun ahi.  
\v 7 Hichun Joshua akapjah jengun, “O Pakai Pathen hiche Amor mite thagamding bepma hi ipi dinga hiche Jordan hi neihinpui galkaiju ham? Hitiding sanga hi Jordan gallang khatna chu neichenden sah jenguleh itiaham?  
\v 8 Pakai, Israel hi agalmitea konna hi ajam theibepma ahileh ipi kaseithei dingham?  
\v 9 Ajeh chu, Canaan mitele hiche gamsunga cheng mite ho hin hiche hi ajahdoh phatnuleh, ama hon eihin umkimvel’un tin hiche gam leisetna konna hi eisuhmang tah louding diuham? Chutengleh aming loupi jaangaina hi itiding hitam?” ati.  
\v 10 Ahinlah Pakaiyin Joshua kom'a h ahin seijin, “Kithoudoh loijin, ipi dinga bohkhupma kijamjeng nahiham?  
\v 11 Israel’in kakitepna asukeh’in sapset changsa thilho aguuvin, eijoulhepmun athilkeo lah’uva akoijun ahi.  
\v 12 Hiche jeh a hi Israel te agalteu masanga dingjou louva gallel’a jamma ahiuve. Tua hi Israel te amaho jeng jonghi suhmang dinga umma ahi tauve. Nalah’uva um sapset changsa thilkeoho chu na suhmang lou’uleh keiman nangho kaumpi louding nahiuve.  
\v 13 Thoudoh’inlang, jing nikho kigotna dingin namite hi amaho le amaho kisuhthengsah’in. Ajeh chu, Pakai Israel Pathen'in aseije, O Israel, sapset changsa thilkeoho chu nalah’uva akiselden nalaije, hiche ho hi nahinlahdoh tokah’uva galmasanga nadin joulou diu ahi.  
\v 14 Jingkah tengleh naphung dungjuijuva nahung kigoldiu ahi, hiteng chuleh Pakaiyin achonsepa chu koiphung penna konham ti ahinphondoh ding ahi. Pakaiyin ahilhendoh phung chu aphungkhaija nahung kigoldohdiu, Pakaiyin achonse phungkhai chu ahin lhendoh ding ahi. Pakaiyin ahinlhendoh phungkhai chu hung kigoldiu achonse insung chu ahin lhendoh ding ahi. Ajonapen’a chu achonse insung mite chu khatkhatna hung kigoldohdiu ahi.  
\v 15 Koi hileh hiche sapset chang thil ana gupen pen ama tah chu aneijouse toh halvam thading ahi, ajeh chu aman Pakai kitepna chu apalkeh’a Israel chunga hitobang hamsetna chu achuhsah ahi,” ati.   
\s1 Achan Chonsetna  
\p
\v 16 Joshua’n jong jingkah langin matah in athouvin Israel phungho chu Pakai maijah ahin goldoh’in ahileh Judah phung chu matdoh ahitai.  
\v 17 Hijeh chun Judah phungkhai chu ahung kigoldoh’in ahileh Zerah phungkhai chu akimandoh kittan ahi. Hichejou chun Zerah insungmi chu ahung kigoldoh’un ahileh Zimri insung chu matdoh ahitai.  
\v 18 Zimri insung mite jouse chu amachang cheh khatkhat’in ahung kigoldoh’un ahileh Achan chu ahin mandoh tauvin ahi.  
\v 19 Hichun Joshua’n Achan kom'a chun hitin aseije, “Kachapa, Israel Pathen loupina hi jana penlang thudihtah seijin, ipi bepseu nanabol hitam phongdoh’inlang, nei seipeh’in, imacha imhihbeh’in” ati.  
\v 20 Achan’in adonbutnin, “Adih’e, Pakai dounan kana chonsetai.  
\v 21 Thil kichomdoh lah a chun, Babylon pon hoitah khattoh, dangka shekel jani toh, shekel sangnga gih sana lhonkhat toh kamun ahileh kadeichan kana kilahtai. Hiche ho chu kaponbuh sungah dangka chutoh tolla kavuijin ahi,” ati.  
\v 22 Hichun Joshua’n akholtoh dingin mi phabep asollin, amaho acheuvin ahileh Achannin asei bangchun thil kiguho chu dangka chutoh akivuitha chu agamu’uvin ahi.  
\v 23 ama hon ponbuh a konchun hiche thilho jouse chu ahinchoijun Israel te leh Joshua kom'a chun ahinchoijun, hiche ho chu Pakai angsung tollhanga chun asekhommun ahi.  
\v 24 Hichun Israel te leh Joshua’n Achantoh, dangka leh ponloupi, sanalhon toh, achapa te le achanute, abongchal ho, asangan ho, akelngoiho le akeltah ho, aponbuh leh athilho jouse chu Achor phaichammah ahin polutnun ahi.  
\v 25 Hichun Joshua’n Achan jah a chun, “Ipi dinga nangin ilah’uva hi hitobang hamsetna hi nahin pohlut ham?” ati. Hichun Israel te jousen Achanleh a insung mite chu song’in aseplih’un atahsa long’u meiyin ahalgam tauve.  
\v 26 Achan chunga chun songlom aseuvin tuni changgeijin aum jing nalaije. Hijeh chun hiche munchu hichenia patchun Lungkhamna Phaicham akisahtan ahi. Hiche pet chun Pakai lunghanna chu adailhatai.   
\c 8  
\s1 Israel ten Ai Khopi Ajo-U  
\p
\v 1 Hichejou chun Pakaiyin Joshua kom'a h chun aseije, “Kicha hih’in, lungthoina jong neihih’in, nasepai ho chu puijinlangAi khopi khu gadelkhumtan, ajeh chu Ai lengpa le amipite, akhopi le agamchu nangma khutna kapehdoh ahitai.  
\v 2 Jericho le alengpao nasuhgam banga amaho jong nasuhgam ding,amavang tuchunga hi agancha houleh anei agou nachomdoh houchu nakilah theiju ahi. Akhopiu nunglanga khun gachangpang tauvin,” ati.  
\v 3 Hiti chun Joshua leh asepaite chu Ai khopi gadelkhum dingin akontouvun ahi. Joshua’n asepaite lah a galsat hatcheh sangsom thum alhengdoh’in jannin asoldoh’in,  
\v 4 Hiti hin thupeh aneiyin ahi: “Nangho cheuvinlang khopi nunglanga khun kinaichan gachangpang’unlang khopi delkhum dingkhun kigosademmin ummun,  
\v 5 Hiteng chuleh kei le kaloiho chengin khopi chu kadellutdiu chutengleh amasa-abang bangchun amaho keiho satdin hungkondoh’un tin chutengleh amaho masanga chu keiho kajamdiu ahi.  
\v 6 Khopia konna chu keihon amaho chu kakidelmang sahdiu, chutengleh ama hon Israel te hi amasa bang banga imasang’uva jamkitna ahi tauve atidiu ahi. Chujou teng chuleh keiho amahoa konna kajam sung uva chu,  
\v 7 Nangho nachangpan nauva konchun hungpotdoh’unlang akhopiu chu nalonvuh jengdiu ahi, na Pakai na Pathen'un nangho khutna nahin pehdohdiu ahi.  
\v 8 Chutengleh Pakaiyin nathupeh bang bangun akhopiu chu meiyin hallha jengun hichu thupeh ahi,” ati.  
\v 9 Hiti chun amaho akipatdoh’un Bethel leh Ai khopi lhumlam kikah achangpanna diu munnah chun ache tauvin ahi. Ahinlah Joshua chu hichejou chun mipi ho toh ngahmunna chun agehkhommun ahi.  
\v 10 Joshua chu jingkah langin matah in akipatnin amite asuthouvin Ai khopi lang ajontan, hichea hin Israel upahon ana juijun ahi.  
\v 11 Joshua chu ama toh umkhom sepaiho chengchutoh khopi maija chun akijotnun sahlanga chun ngahmun asemmun ahi. Amaho leh Ai kikah’a chun phaicham khat aummin ahi.  
\v 12 Chuin aman mi sang nga tobang apuijin Bethel leh Ai khopi kikah khopi lhumlamma chun achangpansah’in ahi.  
\v 13 Hiti chun asepai bulpi penchu khopi sahlanga apansah’in chuleh khopi lhumlamma chun changpangloi akoiyin, Joshua ama tah chu phaichamma chun ageh’in ahi.  
\v 14 Ai lengpan phaicham langa um Israel te chu agahmu phatnin ama le asepaite jouse chun jingpitah in Jordan phaicham gah kigalmun'a munna chun anokhum tauvin ahi. Ahinla khopi nunglanga chun amaho aguh’a chaangpanga aumme tichu aman ahetlou ahi.  
\v 15 Joshua leh Israel sepaite chu gallel tobangin gammang langa chun ajamtauvin ahi.  
\v 16 Hichechun khopi sunga um jouse chu akikoudoh’un abonchauvin amaho chu adeltauvin, hiti chun amaho chu khopia konchun alhemdoh tauvin ahi.  
\v 17 Ai ahilouleh Bethella chun mi khatcha kidalha louvin Israel te chu adelsohkei tauvin ahi. Hiti chun khopi ahomkeuvin adalha tauvin ahi.  
\v 18 Hiche jouchun Pakaiyin Joshua kom'a chun hitin ahin seije, “Natengchao chu domsang’unlang Ai khopi lang ngatsah tauvin, ajeh chu keiman hichekhu nangho khutna kapehdoh ahitai” ati. Hichun Joshua’n akhutna um atengcha chu adomsang’in khopi langchu agah ngatsahtan ahi.  
\v 19 Joshua’n akhut adopsang phatnin changpang ho jouse chu akiselnauva kon'in ahung potdoh’un khopi langa chun alonglut jeng tauvin ahi. Ama hon gangtah in khopi chu alouvin meiyin ahallha tauvin ahi.  
\v 20 Ai khomite chu akinung heijun agah veuvin ahileh, khopia konna meikhu chu vanlaijol langa akitung jengin ahileh chenading helouvin abeiden tauvin ahi. Ajeh chu Israel te gammang langa ana jamlut ho chu ahung kileheijun amaho chu ahinledal tauvin ahi.  
\v 21 Joshua leh Israel te chun apanlah nauchu alolhing’in khopia konchun meikhu akitungdoh tai tichu amu phatnun ahung kileheijun Ai mite chu ahin delkhum tauvin ahi.  
\v 22 Alangkhatnah khopi sunga um Israel te chu ahungpotdoh’un galmi ho chu anunglang uva kon'in ahin delkhum uvin,hiti chun Ai khopi mite chu ajet aveijuva Israel ten aumchinto tauvin amaho alailunga chatmo hellin aumtauve. Israel ten adelkhummun mi khat ajong asohcha ahilouleh ahingdoh’a aum pouve.  
\v 23 Ai lengpa changseh chu ahingin amannun Joshua kom'a h ahin puilutnun ahi.  
\v 24 Israel sepaiten Ai mite chu adel’uva tollhanga um jouse chu athajou phatnun amaho akinung heijun asunga langa um jouse jongchu athatchai heltauvin ahi.  
\v 25 Hiti chun Ai khopi sunga cheng mipite jouse, numeiti pasalti abonchan hiche nikho chun athatgam soh hellun ahileh mi sangsom le sangni alhingin ahi.  
\v 26 Ai khopi sunga cheng jouse chu akisuhmanghel kahsen Joshua’n atengcha chu adomsang jing jengin ahi.  
\v 27 Pakaiyin Joshua athupeh bangin,khopi sunga um agancha houleh anei agouhou chu sumang louvin Israel ten amaho chan dingin akichom tauve.  
\v 28 Hiti chun Joshua’n Ai khopi chu ahallhatan ahileh hichu tuni changgeijin amangthah paitan ahi.  
\v 29 Joshua’n Ai lengpa chu nilhahlang geijin thingchungah anakhaijin, ni ahunglhum phatnin Joshua thupeh dungjuijin atahsa chu thingchunga kon'in alalhauvin, khopi kelkot maija chun anaseplhauvin ahi. Ama hon achunga chun song asetkhummun tuni changgeijin mutheijin aumnalaije.   
\s1 Pakai Kitepna Kithah Suh-Hing  
\p
\v 30 Hijouchun Joshua’n Ebal mol chungah Pakai Israel Pathen kom'a h maicham asemmin, \x + \xo 8:30 \xt Danbu Ni Na 27:2-8\x*  
\v 31 Pakai lhacha Mose’in Israel chate anathupeh Mose daanbua anakijih bangin, thih hemma ana kikheng khalou songtum maicham chungah pumgo thilto leh chamna thilto anabollin ahi. \x + \xo 8:31 \xt Potdohbu 20:25\x*  
\v 32 Hiti chun aman Israel te mitmu changtah chun Mose daan thupeh ho chu song chunga chun anajihdoh’in ahi.  
\v 33 Hiche jouchun Israel te jouse agamsunga pengdenho ahin khopem mi ahiuvin, upaho jouse, vaihom ho jouse le thutanho jouse ahiuvin hopnin akihommun, hopkhat chu Gerazin mol maija adingun, hopkhat chu Ebal mol maija adingun ahi. Ahopni chun aki-angngat touvin akikah uvah Pakai kitepna thingkongpu Levi thempuho chu adingun ahi. Hiche hi Israel mipiten phatthei achanna diuva Pakailhacha Mose thupeh dungjuiya anaboljiu dungjuiya chu abollu ahi. \x + \xo 8:33 \xt Danbu Ni Na 11:29; 27:11-14\x*  
\v 34 Hiche jouchun Mose’n adaan lekhabua anajihlut phatthei bohna le sapsetna ho chu Joshua’n mipi ang’ah chun asimdoh’in ahi.  
\v 35 Mose thupeh thuchengho jouse chu Israel mipi ahung kikhomho leh, nunao chapangho, chuleh alah’uva cheng gamdangmi ho pumma ajahsohkei diuvin asimdoh soh hellin ahi.   
\c 9  
\s1 Gibeon Miten Israel Mite Ajoulhep  
\p
\v 1 Tun Jordan vadung lhumlam gam'a lenghon thilsoh ho hi ajatauvin ahi. Hite ho chu Hit mite, Amor mite, Canaan mite, Perizz mite, Jebus mite lengho, lhumlam molbulla chengho leh twikhanglen pang Lebanon molho chan geija chengho ahiuve.  
\v 2 Hiche lengho hin lungkhattah’a athao jekhomma Joshua leh Israel mite hi kisatpi dingin akiloikhommun ahi.  
\v 3 Ahinlah Gibon miten Joshua’n Jericho leh Ai abolnahi ahetphatnun,  
\v 4 Amaho kihuhdohna dingin lungthim chomkhat agongtauvin ahi. Ama hon Joshua kom'a palai asol’uvin, sakhao luile asesa, jupeng luile akibehthu ho, sangan chunga aheng’un,  
\v 5 ama hon von sesa akivonnun, ponsesa akisillun, kengchot kibehthu akichotnun chuleh neh ding a akipoh’u changlhah chu agopsa le amonsa ahi.  
\v 6 Amaho Gilgalla Israel te ngahmunna ahunglhun phatnun Joshua kom'a chun, “Keiho nangmatoh kichamna thulhuh sem dinga kholgamla tah’a konna hung kahiuve” atiuve.  
\v 7 Israel ten, hiche Hivi mite ho kom'a chun adonbutnun, “Nangho hi anaivella chengmi nahi nahilouvu keihon iti kahet diuham? Anaivella cheng nahikhah uleh keihon nangho toh kichamna thulhuh kanei thei loudiu ahi” atiuve. \x + \xo 9:7 \xt Potdohbu 23:32; 34:12; Danbu Ni Na 7:2\x*  
\v 8 ama hon, “Keiho hi nasohte kahiuve” tin adonbutnun ahi. Ahin Joshua’n, “Nangho koi nahiuva, hoiya konna hung nahiuham?”ati.  
\v 9 ama hon adonbutnun, “Nasohte hi kachenao mun gamla tah’a konna hung kahiuve. Keihon na Pakai na Pathen'u thaneidan Egypt gam'a anatoh ho kanajauvin ahi.  
\v 10 Keihon Jordan solama Amor lengteni leh Heshbon lengpa Sihon le Ashtarothna um Bashan lengpa Og chunga anatoh ho kajauvin ahi. \x + \xo 9:10 \xt Minbu 21:21-35\x*  
\v 11 Hijeh chun kaupahoule kamipite jousen eihin thulhah’un, kholgamla tah jotna dingin nehle chah kipoh’un, Israel mipite chu gakimupiuvin lang hiti hin seijun, ‘keiho nasohte kahiuve keihotoh kitepna neineipiuvin,’ tin gaseijun” atiuve.  
\v 12 “Hiche kachanglhah houhi kain’uva konna kahung kipatdoh uva chu tapkonga konna sapeh’a kahinpoh’u ahin tuhin agobetnin a-ap tan ahin,  
\v 13 Hiche jupengho jonghi kahinthal dimmuva chu thahleh’a ahin, tuhin aluijin a-ehgam tai. Chuleh kavon uleh kakengkoh’u jonghi kalamsao jotnauva konna luigam'a ahitai” atiuve.  
\v 14 Hiti chun Israel ten aneh achah’u chu anakholchil’un, ahinlah Pakai dohna ananei pouve.  
\v 15 Hiche jouchun Joshua in amaho chutoh an ananeipi-in amaho chu anahinghoi tan ahi, khopi sunga alamkai houvin jong hiche kinoptona chu kihahselnan anasudetnun ahi.  
\v 16 Hiche kitepna aneiyu nithum jouvin hiche mite ho hi akomchauva chenga ahibouvui ti ahedoh tauvin ahi.  
\v 17 Israel te chu akholtoh dingin acheuvin nithum sungin akhopi houvachun agalhung tauve. Hiche khopiho chu Gibeon, Kephirah, Beeroth, chule Kiriath-Jearim ahiuve.  
\v 18 Ahinlah Israel ten khopiho chu anokhum tapouvin ahi, ajeh chu Israel lamkaiten, Pakai Israel Pathen min panna kitepna ananeiju ahitai. Israel mipite chu, alamkai houvin chutobang kitepna chu anabol jeh’un achung uvah anaphunnun ahi.  
\v 19 Ahinlah alamkai houvin anadonbutnun “Eihon Pakai Israel Pathen minna kihahselna inaneinao ahitah jeh a amaho chu itohkhah theiloudiu ahitai,  
\v 20 Eihon amaho chu ihinghoidiu ahitai, ajeh chu eihon ikitepnao isuhkeh uleh Pathen lunghanna ichung uva chuding ahi,  
\v 21 Amaho chu ihinghoidiu ahitai” atiuve. Hiti chun ama hon Israel lamkaiten athupeh bangun akhopi sunga twikhai ding leh thingpodin amangcha tauvin ahi.  
\v 22 Joshua’n Gibeon miho chu akoukhommin hitin aseije, “Nanghon ipi dinga neijoulhep uham? Nangho hila kalah uva chenga nahibouvun, ipi dinga gamla tah’a cheng kahiuve natiuham?  
\v 23 Nangho hi sapset chang nahitauvin, hijeh a chu tu apat’a nangho hi ka Pathen'u in na dinga thingchomle twikhaija napan jengdiu ahitai,” atipeh’in ahi.  
\v 24 ama hon adonbutnun, “Pakai na Pathen'un Mose anathupeh dungjuiya hiche gamhi nangho napeh uva chule agamsung mite jouse hi nathagam sohkeidiu ahi ti nasohte keihon kanajauvin ahi. Hijeh chun keihon nangho hi kana kichalheh jengun ahileh hitia hi kanabollu ahi,” atiuve.  
\v 25 “Tun keiho hi nangho khutna um kahi tauve, hijeh chun nadeidan dannin neiboltauvin,” ati.  
\v 26 Hiti chun, Israel ten amaho atha diu chu Joshua’n anajanom tapon ahi.  
\v 27 Ahin hiche nikho chun aman Gibeon mite chu Isael mipite le Pathen'in adeinamun munna a Maicham semna ding twikhai leh thingchommin anapansah tauvin ahi. Hiche hi tuni geija ahintoh jingu ahi.   
\c 10  
\s1 Israel ten Amor Mite Ajo-U  
\p
\v 1 Jerusalem lengpa Adoni-Zedek hin Joshua’n Jericho khopi le alengpau asuhmang banga Ai leh alengpau asuhmanghel chu ajadohtan ahi. Gibeon miten jong Israel te chu akicham piuvin amaho mi in akiheilut tauve tijong ahetan ahi.  
\v 2 Hijeh chun ama leh mipite akichalheh jengun ahi. Ajeh chu Gibeon hi khopi lentah ahin leng khopi dang ho tete ahin chuleh Ai sanga jong khopi lenjo ahin, Gibeon mite jongchu galsatna hatte ahiuve tijong ajan ahi.  
\v 3 Hijeh chun Jerusalem leng Adoni-Zedek chun leng dang ho akoukhommin, amaho chu Hebron lengpa Hoham, Jermeth lengpa Peram, Lachish lengpa Japhia chuleh Eglon lengpa Dabir ahiuve.  
\v 4 “Hungunlang Gibeon mite suhmangna din neihung kithopiuvin,” tin atemmun ahi, ajeh chu “ama hon Joshua leh Israel te toh kichamna asemmun ahi,” ati.  
\v 5 Hijeh chun Amormite leng-nga ho chu galsat dingin akiloikhom tauvin ahi. Hichun ama hon asepaiteu chu akhom khommun Gibeon mite chu ana nokhum tauvin ahi.  
\v 6 Gibeon miten Gilgal ngahmunna um Joshua kom'a chun thulhut ding mi gangtah in asoltauvin ahi. “Nasohte hi neidonda hihbeh’un, gangtah in hungun lang neihung kithopiuvin lang neihung huhdoh’un, ajeh chu thinglhanga cheng Amor lengho akithokhommun eihung delkhum tauve,” atiuve.  
\v 7 Joshua leh asepaite chengse leh galhat laise toh Gilgal adalhauvin Gibeonte kithopi dingin akontauve.  
\v 8 Pakaiyin Joshua kom'a h “Amahokhu kicha hih’un, ajeh chu keiman amaho chunga khu galjona kapeh’u nahi tauve. Amaho khatcha nangho masanga dingngam louding ahiuve.” Tin aseipeh tai.  
\v 9 Joshua chun Gilgalla kon'in jankhovah’in lam ajotnin Amor galmite chu kigingmanlouhel lin anokhum tauvin ahi.  
\v 10 Pakaiyin amaho chu atijatsah’in, hiti chun Israel ten Amor mite chu Gibeon’ah atam a tam athatnun ahi. Hijouchun Israel ten galmi ho chu Beth-horon geijin adellutnun Azekah leh Makkedah lampi geijin abantha peh’un ahi.  
\v 11 Amor mite chu Beth-horon lamlen lammah anungjam peh’un ahileh Pakaiyin vanna kon'in gellom nasatah ajuhlhah sah’in Azekah alhunkahseuvin aban thagam peh’in ahi. Israel ten chemma athasang’un gellin atha atamjon ahi.  
\v 12 Hicheni chun Pakaiyin Israel te chu Amor mite chunga galjona anapen ahi. Joshua’n Israel mipite mitmu changtah in Pakai hengah anataovin, “Gibeon chungah nisa dingden hen chuleh lha jong Aijalon phaicham chungah dingden hen” ati.  
\v 13 Hiti chun nisa leh lha chu Israel nammiten agalmite ajokah seuvin ama muncheh’a adingden lhontan ahi. Hiche thilsoh hi Jashar lekhabua kijihlutna hilouham? Nisa chu vanlaijolla anading dennin nidanga nisalhum ngai bangin analhumpon ahi. \x + \xo 10:13 \xt 2 Samuel 1:18\x*  
\v 14 Pakaiyin amite taona anasanna-ah hitobang hi tumasang leh khonung jengin jong anaumkhapon ahi. Tahbeh mongin Pakaiyin hiche nikho chun Israel te dingin gal anasat peh’in ahi.  
\v 15 Hiche jouchun Joshua leh Israel sepaite chu Gilgal ngahmunnah ahung kilekit tauvin ahi.   
\s1 Israel Miten Amor Leng Nga Ho Athau  
\p
\v 16 Gal kisat laitah chun leng nga ho chu Makeddah songkoa ana kisellun ahi.  
\v 17 Joshua’n amaho chu ahin mudoh phatnun,  
\v 18 Hiti hin thupeh ananeiyin ahi, “Songkohom chu songlentah in sing’unlang lengho chu ahung potdoh louna diuvin apangah chun angah ding mi koijun,” ati.  
\v 19 “Adangse chun galmi ho chu nungdellun lang anung langa kon'in satchap jengun, akhopiu nunglhunsah kit louvin sugam jengun, ajeh chu Pakai na Pathen'un amaho chu nangho khutna napehdoh’u ahitai,” ati.  
\v 20 Joshua le Israel sepaiten galmi ho chu asuhmangsoh kahseuvin athat that jengun ahi. Hiti chun kul kigetkhum akhopiuva jamlut mi themchakhat tailou adangse chu abonchauvin asumangsoh hellun ahi.  
\v 21 Hiche jouchun, Israel te chu Joshua kom Makkedah ngahmunnah bitkeijin akilekitnun ahi. Hiche kalchu koiman Israel te dounan thu themchakhatcha jong aseipoh ngamtapouvin ahi.  
\v 22 Hiche jouchun Joshua’n, “Songkohom kisinna songlentah chu ladoh’unlang leng nga ho chu kakom'a h hinpuijun” ati.  
\v 23 Hichun ama hon leng nga ho chu songko homma konchun ahinpuidoh’un, amaho chu, Jerusalem lengpa, Hebron lengpa, Jermuth lengpa, Lachish lengpa chuleh Eglon lengpa ahiuve.  
\v 24 Amaho chu ahinpuidoh phatnun, Joshua’n gallamkai ho kom'a chun, “Hungun lang nakengphang’un lengho ngongchang hi chonphauvin” ati. Hichun ama hon asei bangchun abollun ahi.  
\v 25 Joshua’n amite kom'a chun, “Kicha hih’un tijatna jong neihih’un, hatnunlang hang’un, ajeh chu Pakaiyin nagalmiteu chunga hitobanga hi abolsohkei ding ahi” ati.  
\v 26 Hiche jouchun Joshua’n leng nga ho chu athatsohkeijin thingphung nga chunga chun akhai sang'in, nilhah chan geijin akhaijun ahi.  
\v 27 Nisalhum kon'in, Joshua thupeh dungjuijin lengho tahsa chu thingchunga kon'in alalhauvin anakiselnau songko homsunga chun aseplutnun ahi. Hijeh chun hiche songkohom chu songlentah ho asekhummun tuni channgeijin aummin ahi.   
\s1 Israel ten Amor Mite Gam Alahbe  
\p
\v 28 Hicheni mama chun Joshua leh Israel ten Madekkah khopi chu alauvin asumang tauve. Aman khopi sunga um jouse chu alengpau pummin athatgammun koimacha ahinghoi pouve. Aman amaho chu athatsoh’in Jericho lengpa atha bangin Madekkah lengpa jongchu athatnin ahi.  
\v 29 Hiche jouchun, Joshua le Israel te chu acheuvin Libnah aganokhum’un ahi.  
\v 30 Hiche jouchun, Pakaiyin hiche khopi le alengpau chu amaho khutnah anapedohtan ahi. Aman khatcha jong hinghoi louvin athatsohkeijin ahi. Hiche jouchun Joshua’n Jericho lengpa atha bangin Libnah lengpa jong chu anathatnin ahi.  
\v 31 Libnah a kon'in Joshua leh Israel te chu Lechish a acheuvin agadelkhum’un ahi.  
\v 32 Hichea jonghin, Pakaiyin Lechish chu amaho khutnah apedoh’in, Joshua’n anini chan nin hijongchu ajouvin Libnah abolna bang bangin athatgam sohkeijin ahi.  
\v 33 Lechish anadelkhum’u chun, Gezar lengpa Haram chu hiche khopi kithopi dingchun asepaite ahinpuijin ahung lhuntan ahi. Ahinlah Joshua’n khatcha jong hinghoi louvin asepaite le amaho chu athatgam tan ahi.  
\v 34 Hijouchun Joshua le Israel sepaite chu acheuvin Eglon agadelkhum’un ahi.  
\v 35 Hicheni chun hiche khopi jongchu alauvin asunga mijouse chu athat tauve. Aman Lechish anabolna bangin abonchauvin anasumang sohkeijin ahi.  
\v 36 Eglon’a kon'in Joshua le Israel te Hebron geijin achetouvun aganokhummun ahi.  
\v 37 ama hon hiche khopi chu alauvin amipite chu alengpau pummin athatnun, khatcha ahinghoi pouvin ahi. Ama hon vella um kho jouse jongchu hitimachun anabollun, Eglon abolna bang bangu chun asunga um mipite jouse chu asumang sohkeijin ahi.  
\v 38 Hiche jouchun Joshua le Israel te chu ahung kinung heijun Debir ahin delkhummun ahi.  
\v 39 Akhopi chu alenpau toh vella kho jouse jongchu alauvin ahi. Aman khatcha hinghoi louvin abonchan anathat gammin ahi. Aman Debir leh alengpa abolna bangle Hebron leh alengpa chuleh Libnah leh alengpa abolna bangin anabollin ahi.  
\v 40 Hiti chun Joshua’n gampumpi chu anajoutan ahi, thinglhang gamkolsunga alenghou le amipiteu, Negiv gamleh, lhumlam molbul gamgi chuleh molnoisuhse ana losoh’in ahi. Pakaiyin ana thupeh bang bangin, aman koimacha hinghoi louvin agamsunga mipi ho jouse ana sumangsohkeijin ahi.  
\v 41 Joshua’n Kedesh barnea-a pat Gaza gei, Goshen khopi vel gamho le Gibeon gamgi geijin mihem ahinthatgam sohkeijin ahi.  
\v 42 Pakai Israel te Pathen chun amite dinga gal ahinsatpeh jeh’in khatvei pansa-a agal konna-ah Joshua’n hiche lengho jouse le agamhou ahin banlah sohkeijin ahi.  
\v 43 Hiche jouchun Joshua le Israel te sepaiho chu Gilgal ngah munnah ahung kilekit tauvin ahi.   
\c 11  
\s1 Israel ten Jabin Le Apanpi Ho Ajo  
\p
\v 1 Hazor lengpa Jabin in thilsoh ho hi ajah phatnin avel'a lengho hi kouna thu athotnin, Madon lengpa Jobab, Shimron lengpa, Aeshaph lengpa,  
\v 2 Sahlam gamkaija lengho jouse, Galibe lhanglang Jordan phaicham gam'a lengho, Galibe molbulla lengho, lhumlam Naphethder lengho,  
\v 3 Solam le lhumlam gamkaija um Canaan lengho, Amor mite lengho, Hit mite, Perizz mite, thinglhang gam'a um Jabus mite, Mizpah gamsunga um Hermon molken suhlanga khopihoa um Hivi mite ho jouse chu akouvin ahi.  
\v 4 Hiche lengho jouse hi galsat dingin ahungkon tauve. Amaho hi ahung kiloikhommun asepai houhi ahintit khommun ahileh alet-lha jengin ahi. Asakol houleh akangtalai hou twikhanglen panga neldiho bangin gamkom alosoh jengun ahi.  
\v 5 Hiche lengho hin athau ajekhommun Israel te satdingin Merom kom'a twipang vellah ngahmun asemmun ahi.  
\v 6 Hichun Pakaiyin Joshua kom'a h hitin ahinseijin, “Amaho khu kichahih’in, jing nikho tuphat tah le hin, amaho hi athisa banga Israel te kahinpehdoh ding ahi. Hiteng chuleh asakolte akeng nasuhbeijuva akangtalai hou nahallhah diu ahi,” ati.  
\v 7 Hiti chun Joshua leh asepaite jousen Merom kom'a twipanga chun alhailutnun gangtah in adelkhum tauvin ahi.  
\v 8 Pakaiyin amaho chu Israel te khutnah ahinpedoh tan, hiti chun ama hon Sidon gamlenlang geileh Misrephath-maim changgei chuleh Mizpah solam phaicham geipeh’in ahindellutnun amaho chu khatcha hinghoi louvin ahin thatsohkeijun ahi.  
\v 9 Pakaiyin aseipeh bang bangin Joshua’n asakolteu keng asatbai peh’in chuleh akangtalai jouseu ahallhah peh’in ahi.  
\v 10 Hiche jouchun Joshua ahung kinunglen Hazor chu alan chuleh alengpau chu athatnin ahi. Phatchomkhat achu Hazor hi hiche lenggam ho jouse bulpi anahin ahi.  
\v 11 Israel ten hiche khopi sunga mihing ching jouse abonchan asumang sohkeijin mi khatcha jong ahing hoipon ahi. Hiti chun Joshua’n khopi chu ahallhatan ahi.  
\v 12 Pakai lhacha Mose’n athupeh bang bangin Joshua’n lengdang ho jouse leh amipiteu abonchan asumang sohkeijin ahi.  
\v 13 Joshua’n anahallhah Hazor tailou Israel ten lhangchunga kitungdoh khopiho chu anahallha pouvin ahi.  
\v 14 Israel ten khopi asuhmang houva achomdoh’u nei le gou ho leh ganchaho chu akilah’un ahi. Ahinla koimacha hinghoi louvin mihing jouse chu athatgam sohkeijin ahi.  
\v 15 Pathen thupeh dungjuiya Mose’n Joshua chu thu anapeh ahi. Hiti chun Joshua’n Pathen thupeh dungjuiya Mose’n anathupeh ho jouse chu atongdoh sohkeijin ahi.   
\s1 Israel ten Gam Alahbe  
\p
\v 16 Hiti hin Joshua’n gamsung pumpi hi anajouvin, thinglhang gam Negiv gampumpi, Goshen khopile vella gampumpi, Kolbul solam gamho, Jordan phaicham gamho, Israel molsangho leh Galilee molbul gamho jouse analasohkeijin ahi.  
\v 17 Tun Israel gamchu Halak mol’apatnin ahung kijedoh’in lhanglanga Seir changgei aphan, chuleh sahlang gam Lebanon phaicham Hermon molbulla Baal-gad changgei ahopmin ahi. Joshua in hiche gam lengho jouse anathatgam sohkeijin ahi.  
\v 18 Hiche tohmolsona dingahin phat sottah gal anadouvun ahi.  
\v 19 Hiche gamhoa hin Gibeon a Hivi mite tailou khatchan Israel te hi ana kichampi pon ahi. Hiche Gibeon miho tailou gamdang miho jouse vangchu anathatgam sohhellun ahi.  
\v 20 Ajeh chu Pakaiyin alungu asuhtah peh’a Israel te chu anakisatpiu ahi. Hijeh achu amaho chu Pakaiyin Mose anathupeh bangin khotona beihellin anasumang’un ahi. \x + \xo 11:20 \xt Danbu Ni Na 7:16\x*  
\v 21 Hichephat sungah hin Joshua’n Hebron thinglhanggam pumpi le Dibar, Anab, Israel te le Judah gamsung pumpia cheng Anak chilhah hojouse ana sumang sohkeijun ahi. Aman amaho hi achennao khopiho jouse pummin anathatgam sohkeijin ahi.  
\v 22 Israel gamsung pumpia Anak chilhahho hi khatcha akihinghoi anaumpouvin ahi. Ahinlah Gaza, Gath gam'a vang amoh themkhat aumnalaijin ahi.  
\v 23 Hichun Pakaiyin Mose anaseipeh bang bangin Joshua’n gamsung pumpi chu analatan ahi. Aman Israel te chu agouchan diuvin aphung aphung dungjuijin anahoppeh’in ahi. Hiti chun galsatna a kon'in gamsung chu ana kicholdo tan ahi.   
\c 12  
\s1 Mose’n Anajo Lengho  
\p
\v 1 Israel ten ana thagammuva agammu analahpeh’u Jordan vadung solam’a cheng lengho chu hiche ho hi ahiuve. Agamlah uchu Armon vadunga konna Hermon molchan ahung kijedoh’in, Jordan phaicham solam gamkaise jong ahopmin ahi. \x + \xo 12:1 \xt Minbu 21:21-35; Danbu Ni Na 2:26—3:11\x*  
\v 2 Heshbon’a cheng Amormi Sihon lengpa jong chu anajouvun ahi, ama lenggam chun Arnon vadung geichinna um Aroer jong ahopmin, hiche chu Arnon vadung akimma konna Jabbek vadunggei ahin hiche hin Ammon mite gamgi melchihna chu ahitai.  
\v 3 Sihon thaneina in Jordan phaicham solam gamkai Galilee twilen sahlanga konna Chitwilen changgei ahopmin, Bath-jeshemath leh Pisgah lhanglang jong ahopphan ahi.  
\v 4 Ashteroth khopile Edrei khopia anacheng Raph-aim mite lah a hingdohpa, Bashan lengpa Og kitipa jong ahin,  
\v 5 Ama hin Hermon molsang pumpi chungleh Salecah gammang toh, chuleh Bashan gamsungsese chunga vaihomma anapanga Geshur mite leh Maacah mite gamgi geija anapehtha ahin, chutengleh Gilead gam kehkhat chunga jong vaihomma, Heshbon lengpa Sihon gamgi geija vai anahom ahi.  
\v 6 Pakai lhacha Mose le Israel chaten hiche leng teni hi akisatpiuvin ajoutauve, hicheahi Pakai lhacha Mose in amani gamsung pumpi chu Reuben chate leh Gad chate chuleh Manasseh phung kehkhat chenna dia anapeh ahi. \x + \xo 12:6 \xt Minbu 32:33; Danbu Ni Na 3:12\x*   
\s1 Joshua Lamkai Na A Anajo Leng Ho  
\p
\v 7 Jordan vadung gal nilhumlam Lebanon phaicham Baal-gad kiti laiya patna Seir niso lamma hung kikhangdoh Halak molsang geija Joshua leh Israel chaten asatgammuva Joshua’n agamjouseu Israel phung mite chenna dia anapehdoh agamnei lengho chu hichenghi ahiuvin,  
\v 8 Agam hop monghi thinglhang gamsung jong, phaigam jong Arabah gamsung jong molken suhsejong, gamthip sungjong, Nageb gamsung jong ahin, Hit mite, Amor mite, Canaan mite Periz mite, Hivi mite chule Jebus gamsung sese chu ahi.  
\v 9 Alengho chu Jericho lengpa ahin Bethel khopia konna Ai khopi lengpa ahin,  
\v 10 Jerusalem lengpa ahin, Hebron lengpa ahin,  
\v 11 Jermuth lengpa ahin, Lachish lengpa khat ahin,  
\v 12 Eglon lengpa ahin, Gezer lengpa ahin,  
\v 13 Debir lengpa ahin, Geder lengpa ahin,  
\v 14 Hormah lengpa ahin, Arad lengpa ahin,  
\v 15 Libnah lengpa ahin, Adullam lengpa ahin,  
\v 16 Makkedah lengpa ahin, Bethel lengpa ahin,  
\v 17 Tappuah lengpa ahin, Hepher lengpa ahin,  
\v 18 Aphah lengpa ahin, Lasher’on lengpa ahin,  
\v 19 Madon lengpa ahin, Hazor lengpa ahin,  
\v 20 Shimron-meron lengpa ahin, Ach-shaph lengpa ahin,  
\v 21 Taunach lengpa ahin, Magiddo lengpa ahin,  
\v 22 Kadesh lengpa ahin, Carmel molla Jokni’am lengpa ahin,  
\v 23 Naphatdor gam'a Dor lengpa ahin, Galilee gam'a Goi’im lengpa ahin,  
\v 24 Tirzah lengpa khatjong ahin, abonchan leng somthum le khat chu anajouvin ahi.   
\c 13  
\s1 Lahbe Ding Gam Ho  
\p
\v 1 Joshua chu atehtan akum jong atamlheh tan, hichun Pakaiyin akom'a hiti hin thu ahin seijin ahi, “Nangla natehtan, nakumjong atamthim lhehtan ahinlah gamlahding hi atamlheh jeng nalaijin ahi.  
\v 2 Gamlahding vatnalai ho chu Philistine te gamleh Geshur gamho sese jong ahinalaije.  
\v 3 Egypt solam’a um Sihor gam'a konna Ekron solam gamgi changgei (Canaan gammia kisimma ahi) chuleh Philistine vaipote nga ho, Gaza, Ashdod, Gath, leh Ekron jong ahopmin chuleh Avvit mite gamjong ahopthan ahi.  
\v 4 Lhanglam gam'a ahileh Canaan mite gampumpi ahin, chule Sidon mite gamsunga Maarah changgei leh Aphek gei, chujongleh Amor mite gamgi changgei ahin,  
\v 5 Gebal mite leh Lebanon gampumpi, nisolam lengsese, Baal-gad khopi apat Hermon molsang nisolam gei ahin, Hamath khopi jotna kotphung gei ahithai,  
\v 6 Chule Lebanon apatna Misrephothmaim changgeija mite ahiuvin, Sidon mite pumpummin thinglhang gam'a cheng thinglhang mite aboncha ahiuve. Mihem hijat hi aboncha keima mong mong’in Israel chate masanga kadelmang ding ahi, nangma kahilla kathupeh bang bangchun agamhi Israel ten alouva achenpha diuvin hoppeh poupou tan. \x + \xo 13:6 \xt Minbu 33:54\x*  
\v 7 Chuti ahijeh chun nangman tuhin hiche gamhi Israel phung ho leh Manasseh phung kehkhat goulo din hoppehtan” ati.   
\s1 Jordan Luigal Nisolam Gam Kihop  
\p
\v 8 Manasseh phung kehkhat leh Reuben chate chule Gad chate chun Pakai lhacha Mose’n apehsao Jordan vadung gal nisolam gamsung chu agoulo achan diuvin akisem tauve. \x + \xo 13:8 \xt Minbu 32:33; Danbu Ni Na 3:12\x*  
\v 9 Agamchu Arnon phaicham pamchinna Aroer khopia pat phaicham lailunga khopi changgei ahipeh’in Madaba gam dokhang banga kikhangdohlai jong ahopsohkeijin Dibon chan gei ahi.  
\v 10 Heshbon lengvaipo Amor mite lengpa Sihon khopi jouse jong ahin Ammon mite gamgi chan gei ahi.  
\v 11 Chujongleh Gilead gam ahin, Geshur mite leh Ma-acath mite lhangmang geijin ahopmin Hermon molsang pumpi jong ahin, chuleh Bashan pumpi ahop peh’in Salicah gei ahipeh’e.  
\v 12 Ashtaroth khopi le Edrei khopia lengvaipoa anapang Bashan gamsunga Og lengpa lenggam abonchan ahopmin hiche Og kitipa hi Repham mite lah a achangseh a anahingdoh mikhat jong ahi, hichengse hi Mose in gal’a akisatpia ajosohkeija adelmang sohkei ahi.  
\v 13 Ahinlah Israel chaten Geshur mite leh Ma-acath mite chu tuni geijin Israel lailunga acheng cheng tauvin ahi.   
\s1 Levi Phungmite Chan ding  
\p
\v 14 Mose in goulo ding apehlouhel phung chu Levi phungbou ahitai. Pakaiyin aseipeh banga Pakai Israel Pathen henga govam thilto chengse chu Levi te chan ding agoulo diuva ummah ahi. \x + \xo 13:14 \xt Danbu Ni Na 18:1\x*   
\s1 Reuben Phungmite Gam Kipe  
\p
\v 15 Reuben chate phung jongchu Mose in ama ama insung dungjui cheh’in agoulo diu anapei.  
\v 16 Hijechun Reuben phung mite gamgi hopchu ahileh Arnon phaicham pamchinna kisa Aroer khopia kipan chuche phaicham lailunga khopi chan gei ahin, Medeba gam dokhang banga kikhangdoh chengse jong ahopme.  
\v 17 Heshbon khopi jong ahin dokhang banga kikhangdoh gamsunga Heshbon khopi jouse chutoh ahithai, akhopi ho chu Dibon leh Bamoth leh Bamoth-baal, Bethbaalmeon jong ahin,  
\v 18 Jahaz jong Kedemoth jong Mepha-ath jong,  
\v 19 Kiriatha-im jong Sibmah jong phaikola thinglhang vumma Zereth Shahar jong,  
\v 20 Bethpoer jong Pisgah lhang panglang sese jong Beth-jishimoth jong ahi.  
\v 21 Hicheng lah a hi dokhang langa kido gamsunga khopi jouse leh Amor mite lengpa Sihon lenggam pumpi ahithai, hiche Sihon hi Heshbon khopia lengvaipoa anapang ahin Mose in hiche Sihon hileh Midian lamkai ho Evi, Rekem, Zurle Hur chule Reba kiti Sihon lengpa chapa te agamsunga chengse chu anajotha ahitai.  
\v 22 Baalam kitipa Beor chapa phunsan thempa jongchu Israel chaten midang atha lah uva chu chemjamma asatlihthau ahitan ahi.  
\v 23 Hiti hin Reuben chate gamgi chu Jordan vadung hi ahiyenge. Hiche hi Reuben chate goulo ahin, ama ama insung dungjui cheh’a khopiho jong khoneoho jong chentha cheh ahiuve.   
\s1 Gad Phungmite Gam Kipe  
\p
\v 24 Gad phung jongchu Mose’in ama ama insung dungjui cheh in goulo gam anapei.  
\v 25 Chule Gad chate gamgi hopsese chu, Jazer kho ahin, Gilead gam khopi chengse ahin, Ammon mite gamsung kehkhat toh ahin, chule Rabbah nisolama um Aroer khopi gei ahiye.  
\v 26 Chuin Heshbon khopia pat Ramath-mizpeh le Betonim khopi gei ahin, chule Mahanaim khopia pat Lo-debar gamsung gei ahiye.  
\v 27 Chutengleh phaichamma ahileh Beth-haram ahin, Beth-nimrah ahin, Succoth ahin, chule Zaphon le Heshbon lengpa Sihon lenggamsunga adang jouse toh ahitha’n, Jordan gamgia vadung gamgia panga Jordan vadung gallama niso lamma Galilee twilen tolam among lamtoh kimatpai ahitai.  
\v 28 Hiche hi ama ama insung dungjui cheh’a akhopi jouse leh akhoneo jouse pumpumma kihoppeh Gad chate gamchan agoulou ahi.   
\s1 Solam’a Manasseh Phungkeh Gam Kipe  
\p
\v 29 Manasseh phung kehkhat jong chu Mose in goulo gam anapen agam goulo chu Manasseh phung kehkhat jong ama ama insung dungjui cheh’in akihom’uvin ahi.  
\v 30 Manasseh phung kehkhat gamhop lhang le molchu Mahanaim a ahung kipannin, Bashan gamsung jouse ahin adeh deh’in Bashan gam'a Og lengpa lenggam pumpitoh Bashan gamsunga um Jair kho lehndom jouse jong ahin, abonchan khopi somgup jen alhing’in,  
\v 31 Gilead kikahtoh, Asharoth toh Edrei toh ahin, abkonna hi Bashan gamsunga Og lengpa lenggama khopi jong ahiuve, hijat hi Manasseh chapa Makir chate leh Makir phungmite alangkhat kihomma ama ama insung dungjuiya chan kipesohkei ahiuve.  
\v 32 Gam goulo hijatpihi Mose in Jordan vadung gal Jericho khopi nisolam Moab phaichamma anahopdoh ahitai.  
\v 33 Levi phung vangchu Mose in goulo gam achansah poi, ajeh chu Pakaiyin ajah uva aseisa banga Pakai Israel Pathen chu Levi te goulo ahiyenge. \x + \xo 13:33 \xt Minbu 18:20; Danbu Ni Na 18:2\x*   
\c 14  
\s1 Jordan Luigal Lhumlam Gam Kihop  
\p
\v 1 Canaan gamsunga Eleazer thempupa leh Nun chapa Joshua chuleh apu apau, insung lhah dungjuiya Israel chate phung jousea lamkai hon Israel chate goulo dia ana hoppeh u, Israel chaten jong akisan cheh agoulo’u gamsung cheh chu hichenghi ahi.  
\v 2 Israel phungkole akeh khat gam kihop dingdolla Pakaiyin Mose thu anapeh bang bangin agoulo diu gamchan chu vang kisana kihom anahi. \x + \xo 14:2 \xt Minbu 26:52-56; 34:13\x*  
\v 3 Israel phungni le phung kehkhat vang chu Mose in agoulo diuva Jordan vadung gallama gam anapehsa ahitai, Levi phungmite chu Israel lah a gouloding gam apeh lou mong mong ahi. \x + \xo 14:3 \xt Minbu 32:33; 34:14,15; Danbu Ni Na 3:12-17\x*  
\v 4 Chujongleh Joseph Chate chu phungni akisouvin, Manasseh le Ephraim ahi, Levi te vangchu gamsunga amaho chan ding gam akipepon, achenna diu khopi mai ail eh gancha vahna diu hamhing gamtoh athilkeo u maimaibou ahi.  
\v 5 Pakaiyin Mose ahilla athupeh bang bangin Israel chaten abolsohkeiyin gam akihom tauve.   
\s1 Caleb Hebron Khopi Kipe  
\p
\v 6 Gilgal achun Judah chate thalheng in mi phabep Kenizz mi kitipa, Jephunneh Chapa Caleb lamkai nan ahung kitol touvin,Joshua jah a chun hitin aseiyin, “Kadesh Barnea kiti munna chu kei le nang chung chang thudolla Pakaiyin Pathenmi Mose jaha ipi anaseipeh geldoh in. \x + \xo 14:6 \xt Minbu 14:30\x*  
\v 7 Pakai lhacha Mose Kadesh-barnea mun'a konna Canaan gamvelhidia eina sol chun keima kum somli kana lhingtai, hichea chun keiman ka lungsunga kahet chanchu Mose henga thu kahin lhutnin ahi. \x + \xo 14:7 \xt Minbu 13:1-30\x*  
\v 8 Ahinla kachepi khompi kasopiho chun gamptep gam jotlutding chu mipi lungthim asulhadeh jengun ahi, ahinlah keivangin Pakai ka Pathen chu lungthim pumpin kajui lhum keijin ahi.  
\v 9 Hijeh chun hiche nikho chun, Mose akihahsel in aseitan ahi,”Tahbehin nakengphang achotphana muntinchu a-itih a nang le na chilhah te goullo dinga nachan ding ahi, ajeh chu nangin Pakai ka Pathen chu najuilhum keiyin ahi” einatin ahi. \x + \xo 14:9 \xt Minbu 14:24\x*  
\v 10 “Tun vetan, Pakiyin aseibang bangin Israel gamthip gam'a akitolle laiya Pakiyin Mose jah a hiche thu anaseija pat tuphat geihin keima eihing hoinalaiyin, tuhin kum somgetlenga kalhingtai.  
\v 11 Tuni geihin Mose’n gamvea einasol lai bangin katha ahat nalaiyin, hichepetna katha hat bang bangin kahat nalaiyin, galkon theileh gallamkaithei kahi nalaije.  
\v 12 Chuti ahijeh chun Chuche nikhoa Pakaiyin eina teppeh bang bangchun hiche molkhu neipetan. Gamvellhi ichelai’juva thupitah a khopi kul kigetkhum ho sunga cheng Anak chilhah ho chu nahen ahi. Ahiyeng vang'in Pakaiyin eiumpileh Aman aseibang banga amahokhu kajoa kanodoh ding ahi,” ati.  
\v 13 Hiti chun Jephunneh Chapa Caleb chu Joshua’n phatthei aboh in ama chantum dingin Hebron chu anapetan ahi.  
\v 14 Hiti hin, Hebron chu Jephunneh Chapa Caleb le achilhah te achengden tauvin ahi, ajeh chu aman Israel Pakai Pathen chu anajuilhum keijin ahi.  
\v 15 (Tumasang chun Hebron hi Kiriath-arba ana kitin ahi. Hiche hi Anak chilhah galhat penpa Arba minna kisah ahi) Hiti chun gamleiset chu galdouna a kon'in anakicholdotan ahi.   
\c 15  
\s1 Judah Phungmite Gam Kipe  
\p
\v 1 Judah phung sunga chun a insung dungjui cheh a achandiu chu hiti hin akihoppehin ahi. Zin gammanga Edom gamgi lhanglang chu alhangnung penna gamgi chu ahitai.  
\v 2 Chuleh lhanglang gamgichu lhanglang ngat twikolla pat Chitwilen lang chan gei ahi.  
\v 3 Hiti chun Akrabbim lhanglang ninga achesuh in Zin gam ahopan, Kadesh-barnea lhanglang ning langa akaltouvin, chuleh Hezron ahopan chuleh Adar langa akaltouvin chuleh Karka vel kollang ahopan ahi.  
\v 4 Hichea kon chun Azmon lang ajonnin achainan Egypt vadung langa achepeh in Mediterranean twikhanglen chan gei alhungin ahi. Hiche hi amaho lhanglang gamgi chu ahitai.  
\v 5 Chutengleh solam gamgichu Chitwilen chan gei akilhung dohin Jordan kom chan geijin achepehin ahi. Sahlang gamkaiya gamgi chu Jordan vadung ola chun akipannin. Chitwilen achun alonglutnin ahi.  
\v 6 Beth-hoglah-a kon'in achetouvin Beth-arabah sahlang geijin ache in Bohan songphung gei achu gamgi kilhungdoh peh in ahi.(Bohan chu Reuben chapa ahi).  
\v 7 Hichea patna gamgi chu Achor phaicham Dabir la konna chetoupeh a Gilgal langa chetouva ahi. Hiche hi Adummin kaltouna masang ahi. Gamgi chu En-shamesh twitah geijin achepeh in En-rogel munnah akichaijin ahi.  
\v 8 Gamgi chun Ben Hinnom phaicham chu apal galkaijin erusalem khopi kitundohna munlang Jebus mite chenna lhangsuh a chun akilhungdoh peh in ahi.  
\v 9 Hicheakon chun gamgi molsang chung vumma kon'in ahung kijidoh in, Nephtoah twiputna chan geijin achetoupeh in, hichea kon chun Ephron lhang khopiho chan geijin akilhunglutnin ahi. Hicheakon chun Baalah (Hichu Kiriath-jearim akiti’e) akiheilut’a ahi.  
\v 10 Gamgi chun Baalah lhumlam avellin Seir thinglhang chu ajonlutnin, Jearim molsang sahlama Kesalon khopi sung ahohpan, chuin Beth-shemesh langa akigolsuh in, Timnah lang ajotpaije  
\v 11 Hichea konchun gamgi chu Ekron sahlang thinglhang chu ajonlutnin hichea kon chun Shikkeron leh Baalah lhanglang ajonnin ahi.Hichebanna chun Jabneel ahohpan Mediterranean twikhanglennah akichaijin ahi.  
\v 12 Lhumlam gamgi chu Mediterranean twikhanglenpangjui chu ahipehe.Hiche hi Juda phung bahkaiho gamgi chu ahi.   
\s1 Caleb In Hebron Le Debir Khopi Alah  
\p
\v 13 Pakaiyin Judah gambihkhatchu Jephunneh chapa Caleb apehdingin Joshua chu thu apen ahi.Hijeh chun Caleb chu Kiriath-arba (Hebron tina ahi) khopichu apen ahi. Hiche Hebron hi Anak apu apateu minkhatna anakiminvo ahi. \x + \xo 15:13 \xt Thutan Vaihom Ho 1:20\x*  
\v 14 Caleb chun Anak chate Sheshai, Ahiman leh Talmai chilhah hon thum ho chu ana no doh in ahi.  
\v 15 Hichea kon chun Debir khopi (tumasanga chu Kiriath-sepher kiti ahi) achengte galkisatpi din anakontai.  
\v 16 Caleb min aseijin, “Koi hileh Kiriath-sepher nokhumna galla galjou penchu kachanu Acsah akichen pidinga kapeh ding ahi” ati.  
\v 17 Caleb sopipa Kenaz chapa Othniel chun aga joutan ahileh Acsah chu Othniel ji ahung hitai.  
\v 18 Acsah in Othniel akichenpi chun amanun apa kom'a loumun khat thumdin ajipa chu angeh in ahi.Amanu asangan chunga konna akum lhahchun Caleb in “Ipi nadeiham?” tin anadonge.  
\v 19 Amanun aseijin, “Negev ma gamkhat bon neipeh ahitah leh twinah khatjong neipehthan ati.” Hiti chun Caleb injong sahlang twinah leh lhanglang twinah khat apen ahi.   
\s1 Judah Phungmite Khopi Ho  
\p
\v 20 Hiche hi Judah phungin abahkai abahkai dungjuiya a insung chehuva achenna diuva kipe munchu ahi.  
\v 21 Judah khopiho chu Edom gamgi chin anoinung penna umho chu: Kabzeel, Eder, Jagur,  
\v 22 Kinah, Dimonah, Adadah,  
\v 23 Kedesh, Hazor, Ithnan,  
\v 24 Ziph, Telem, Bealoth,  
\v 25 Hazor-hadattah, Kerioth-hezron (Hichu Hazor tina ).  
\v 26 Amam, Shema, Moladah,  
\v 27 Hazar-gaddah, Heshmon, Beth-pelet,  
\v 28 Hazar-shual, Beersheba, Biziothiah,  
\v 29 Baalah, Iim, Ezem,  
\v 30 Eltolad, Kesil, Hormah,  
\v 31 Ziklag, Madmannah, Sansannah,  
\v 32 Lebaoth, Shilhim, Ain chuleh Rimmon–agoma khopi somni le ko chule avel'a khojouse ahi.  
\v 33 Lhumlam molbulla um khopi ho chengse jonghi Judah anakipe ho chu ahiuve: Eshtaol, Zorah, Ashnah,  
\v 34 Zanoah, En-gannim, Tappuah, Enam,  
\v 35 Jarmuth, Adullam, Socoh, Azekah,  
\v 36 Shaaraim, Adithaim, Gederah chuleh Gederothaim – khopi somleli toh avel'a khoho jouse ahi.  
\v 37 Hiche tilou vinjong, Zenan, Hadashah, Migdal-gad,  
\v 38 Dilean, Mizpeh, Joktheel,  
\v 39 Lachish, Bozkath, Eglon,  
\v 40 Cabbon, Lahmam, Kitlish,  
\v 41 Gederoth, Beth-dagon, Naamah chuleh Makkedah – khopiho somlegup avel'a khojouse jong ahi.  
\v 42 Hiche tilouvin jong, Libnah, Ether, Ashan,  
\v 43 Iphtah, Ashnah, Nezib,  
\v 44 Keilah, Aczib chule Mareshah – khopi ko ho leh avel'a khoho jouse ahiuve.  
\v 45 Judah phung miten atoupha diuva kipe gamho chu Ekron leh avel'a khoho jong ahopmin ahi.  
\v 46 Ekron na kon chun lhumlam gamgi chin geijin akijedohin Ashdod kom'a khogeiho leh khoho jouse jong ahop’in ahi.  
\v 47 Ashdod avel'a khojouse chule Gaza le asunga khohojouse, Egypt vadung leh Mediterranean twikhanglen pang chan gei ahopmin ahi.  
\v 48 Judah chanchu noija thinglhang khopiho: Shamir, Jattir, Socoh,  
\v 49 Dannah, Kiriath-sannah (Hichu Debir tina),  
\v 50 Anab, Eshtemoh, Anim,  
\v 51 Goshen, Holon chuleh Giloh – khopi somlekhat toh avel'a khoho ahiuve.  
\v 52 Chukitleh Arab khopi ho jong ahop in ahi: Dumah, Eshan,  
\v 53 Janim, Beth-tappuah, Aphekah,  
\v 54 Humtah, Kiriath-arba (hichu Hebron tina), chuleh Zior – khopi koleh avel'a khoho ahiuve.  
\v 55 Hichetilou jongchun, Maon, Carmel, Ziph, Juttah,  
\v 56 Jezreel, Jokdeam, Zanoah,  
\v 57 Kain, Gibeah chuleh Timnah – khopi som leh vella khoho ahiuve  
\v 58 Hiche banna jong chun Halhul, Beth-zur, Gedor,  
\v 59 Maarath, Beth-anoth chuleh Eltekon – khopi gup leh vella khoho ahiuve.  
\v 60 Kiriath-baal (Hichu Kiriath-jearim tina ahi) chuleh Rabbah – khopi ni leh avel'a khoho ahiuve.  
\v 61 Gamthip gam'a khopiho chun Beth-arabah, Middin, Secacah,  
\v 62 Nibshan, Chi khopi len chule En-gedi – khopi gup leh vella khoho ahiuve.  
\v 63 Ahin Judah phungin Jerusalem ma cheng Jebu mite ana nodoh joupouvin, hijeh chun tuni chan geijin Jebu mitehi Judah te toh acheng khom jengun ahi. \x + \xo 15:63 \xt Thutan Vaihom Ho 1:21; 2 Samuel 5:6; 1 Thusimbu 11:4\x*   
\c 16  
\s1 Lhumlam Manasseh Le Ephraim Gam Kipe  
\p
\v 1 Joseph chilhah ho chan ding kipeho chu Jericho kom'a Jordan vadunga kon'in ahung kilhungin, Jericho twinah solam, gamthip gam hoipen Bethel thinglhanga alutnin ahi.  
\v 2 Bethel a kon'in Ataroth apalgal kaijin Arki mite gam'a alutnin ahi.  
\v 3 Hichea konchun lhumlama akum suhin Japhlet mite gam'a alutnin Beth-horon chan geijin alutnin, chea kon chun Gezer lah alutnin Mediterranean twikhanglen'a alut galkaijin ahi.  
\v 4 Hiche hi Joseph chate Manasseh leh Ephraim insungmite gamlo dinga kipe ahi.   
\s1 Ephraim Gam Kipe  
\p
\v 5 Noija ho hi Ephraim phung abahjam hojouse achandiova kipe ahi. Amaho gamloding solam gamgi chu Ataroth-addar a kipan ahi. Hichea kon chun Beth-horon sahlanga alutnin,  
\v 6 Chujouvin Mediterranian twikhanglen'ah alutnin ahi. Micmethath sahlanga kon'in, gamgi chu ahung kon'in Taanath-shiloh ahopan solam Janoah ajonnin ahi.  
\v 7 Janoah a kon'in lhanglang ahin jonnin Ataroth le Naarah na alutnin Jericho hopan Jordan vadunga atangin ahi.  
\v 8 Tappuah a patnin gamgichu lhumlam ma akilhung ngin Kanah vacha a kon'in Mediterranian twikhanglen na alutnin ahi. Hiche hi Ephraim phung bahkai jouse gamloding chu ahi.  
\v 9 Hiche banna chun khopi phabep le vella khoho Manasseh phung kehkhat chan dinga ana kipe jongchu Ephraim phung dingin akikoipih tan ahi.  
\v 10 ama hon Gezer akon'in Canaan mite chu ananodoh joupouvin ahinlah Gezer mite chu tuni chan geijin Ephraim mite sohin apang taove. \x + \xo 16:10 \xt Thutan Vaihom Ho 1:29\x*   
\c 17  
\s1 Lhumlam Manasseh Gam Kipe  
\p
\v 1 Gamloding kihopna abannachu Joseph chillhah chamasa Manasseh phung akehkhat chu akipen ahi. Makir Manesseh chamasa chu Gilead dia apa ahi. Ama chilhah ho hi galhatmi ahijehun Jordan solam gamkaija um Gilead le Bashan chu anakipesa ahi.  
\v 2 Hiti chun Jordan lhumlam gamkai Abizer, Helek, Asreil, Sechom, Hepher, chuleh Shemida ho hi Manasseh phungkhai sung lah a avatnalai insungho chan ding ahi. Hiche bahkhai ho hin Joseph cha Manasseh chilhah pasal ho thalheng ahiuve.  
\v 3 Ahiyeng vang'in Manasseh chapa Makir, Makir chapa Gilead, Gilead chapa Hepher, Hepher chapa Zelophahad chu cha neilou ahin, aman chanubou aneiyin amaho minchu Malah, Noah, Haglah, Milcah chuleh Tirzah ahiuve.  
\v 4 Hiche numei ho hi, thempupa Eleazer, Nun chapa Joshua, chuleh Israel lamkaiho kom'a h ahungun hitin ahungseijun ahi, “Pakaiyin, Mose jah a eiho leh kasopi teu pasal ho gamlodi eipehdiovin thupeh anapen ahi” atiove. Hijeh chun Joshua’n jong amaho chu Pakai thupeh banga apa-ngahteu chan bangin gamchu anapen ahi. \x + \xo 17:4 \xt Minbu 27:1-7\x*  
\v 5 Hijeh chun Manasseh chan apumpi chu Jordan vadung galla Gilead leh Bashan gamchan banna chu gamchan oma hung lhingtan ahi.  
\v 6 Ajeh chu Manasseh chilhah numei ho jong pasal chilhah chanto kibanga achanjeh’u ahi. (Gilead gamchu Manasseh chilhah pasal amoh ho kipeh ahi).  
\v 7 Manasseh phung gamgichu Asher gamgi hina kon'in Secheme kom Micmethath chan gei jin ahung kikholutnin ahi. Hichea konchun gamgichu Micmethath’a kon'in achesuhin Tappuah twinah putna kom'a chenna munho geijin ahung kilhung lut in ahi.  
\v 8 Tappuah velkolla gamho chu Manasseh chan ahi. Manasseh gamgi a um Tappuah khopi tah vang chu Ephraim phung mite chan ahi.  
\v 9 Tappuah twinah putna akon'in Manasseh gamgi chun Kanah vadungneo chu ajuijin Meditteranean twikhanglen'ah alutnin ahi. Hiche vadungneo lhanglanga khopi phabep chu Manasseh gamsung ahi, ahinla hiche ho chu atah beh’in Ephraim phungho chan ahi.  
\v 10 Alhanglhoninvang, hiche vadungneo lhanglam gamchu Ephraimte chan ahi, chuleh vadungneo sahlang gamchu Manasseh te chan ahi. Manasseh gamgi vadungneo sahlang gamkai chutoh akilhonin Mediterranean nah a atangin ahi. Manasseh sahlang chu Asher gam ahin chuleh sahlang vangchu Issachar gam ahi.  
\v 11 Ahivangin Issachar le Asher gamgi sunga um khopi ho, Beth-shan khopi, Ibleam khopi, Dor khopi (Hichu Naphoth-dor), Endor, Taanach khopi chule Megiddo khopi ho leh agamsunga cheng hojouse chu Manasseh chan din anakipe tan ahi.  
\v 12 Ahinlah Manasseh chilhah chengse chun hiche khopi ho chu analalut joupou vin ahi. Ama hon Canaan mite chu anadel-mang jou pouvin tuni geijin aum nalaijun hai. \x + \xo 17:12 \xt Thutan Vaihom Ho 1:27,28\x*  
\v 13 Ahinlah khonunga Israel te ahung hatdoh phatnuvin Canaan mite chu soh in amang tauvin ahi. Ahinlah agam sung uva kon'in anodoh joupouvin ahi.   
\s1 Ephraim Le Lhumlam Manasseh Gam Thumbe  
\p
\v 14 Joseph chilhah te Joshua kom'a h ahungun hiti hin ahung dong’ui, “Pakaiyin hibanga eipunsahuva ipi dinga kachenna dio gamhi chan khatbou neipeh ham?”  
\v 15 Joshua’n adonbutnin “Nangho natamlheh jengtah uva Ephraim thinglhang gam nangho dinga aneotah a ahileh hiche Periz mitele Reph mite channa gammang lahkhu nangho dingin gakisuhtheng tauvin atipeh in ahi.”  
\v 16 Joseph chilhah te chun adonbutnin, “Thinglhang gamhi keiho dingin alhing joupoi katiu hi atahbeh ahi. Ahinlah Canaan mite gamnomma cheng ho leh Jezreel phaichamma um ho hin thih sakol kangtalai aneiyun, amaho hi keihon kadoudio vin ahahsa valle atiove.”  
\v 17 Hichun Joshua’n Joseph chilhah te Ephraim le Manasseh phungmi te ho kom'a h hitin aseije “Nangho hi natammuve nahatlheh jeng taove ahileh nangho dingahi chan khatval kipeding nahiuve.  
\v 18 Thinglhang gammang lahkhu nangho nachan bediu ahi. Nanghon nasuhtheng nom chanun gakisuhthengun agam lapen aningkoi chan geijin galo tauvin phaichamma Canaan mite jeng jongkhu hatlheh uhenlang thih sakol kangtalai neijongleho ganodoh tauvin,” ati.   
\c 18  
\s1 Gam Amoh Cheng Kikhopna  
\p
\v 1 Tunvang gamsung chu Israel te khut noiya uma ahitai, Israel mite chu abonchauvin Shiloh a akikhomun hichea chun kikhopna ponbuhkhat atungdohn tauve.  
\v 2 Ahinlah hichea chun phung sagi ho chu alodiu chennagam kipeloulai aum nalaijin ahi.  
\v 3 Hichun Joshua’n amaho chu adongin, “Napu napa teu Pakai Pathen'in nalodiuva napeh u gam nachandiu chu itih chan gei nanga diuham?” ati.  
\v 4 “Phungkhat a mithum cheh hinlhengdoh unlang keiman amaho chu gam vetoh dingin gahsol intin, amaho cheuvin tin amaho cheh in alodiu gamchu hinvetoh untin keikom'a thu ahin lhut kit diu ahi.  
\v 5 Judah ten achannu lhanglam gamleh Joseph in achennao sahlang gam panglouva ama hon agamvet uchu hop sagi’a ahopdiu ahi.  
\v 6 Hitia chu ama hon agamvet u ajihlutnao chu keikom'a ahin choilutdiu, aphungdungjuiya achondiu akipehtheina dinga keiman Pakai Pathen angsung’a vang theng kasanding ahi.  
\v 7 “Levi te chun gamchan aneiloudiu ahi. Amaho chan ding chu Pathen thempu kinbol chu hi ding ahi. Chuleh Gad, Reuben leh Manasseh phung kehkhat ho chu gam chanbeloudiu ahitai. Ajeh chu Pakai lhacha Mose’n amaho chu Jordan vadung solam gamkaija anapehsa ahitan ama hon gamchan chu akimusao ahitai,” ati.  
\v 8 Amaho gam gakholtoh ding leh gajihdoh dinga akipatdoh uchun Joshua’n hitin thupeh ananeiyin ahi, “Cheuvinlang agamchu gakholtoh unlang kichihtah in hinjihdoh un. Chujou teng kakom'a hungun, huting keiman Shiloh munna Pakai angsung’a vangsan na kanei ding chuteng aphung dungjui a agam chu kahoppehdiu nahiuve” ati.  
\v 9 Miho chun gampumpi chu agakholtoh dungjuijin ahin jihdoh un khopi ding leh khoneoding agongtoh un hopsagi in ahommun lekhabua ajihkit un Shiloh ngahmunna Joshua kom'a ahinpo lutnun ahi.  
\v 10 Chuleh Shiloh achun Joshua'n Pakai angsung’a vangsan’na aneiyin hoilai munchu koi phungpen chang dingham ti avetan ahi.   
\s1 Benjamin Phungmite Gam Kipe  
\p
\v 11 Vang kivetna-a chan masa chu Benjamin phunga alhungin ahi. Hiche chan hi Judah le Joseph gamchan kikah’a um gam chu ahi.  
\v 12 Benjamin channa sahlang gamgi chu Jordan vadunga hung kipan ahin, Jericho sahlang juilang ajonnin, hiti chun lhumlama thinglhang gamleh Beth-aven ahin pal galkaijin ahi.  
\v 13 Hiche apatin gamhi chu Luz (Bethel tina) lhanglama achepeh in hijouchun achesuh in noinung Beth-horon lhanglam thinglhang chunga um Ataroth-addar munna alutnin ahi.  
\v 14 Gamgi chu ahung kileheijin lhanglang ajonsuh in Beth-horon maingat thinglhang lhumlam gei hina alutnin Kiriath-baal (Keriath-jearim tina) khokhatna atangin ahi. Hiche hi Judah phung khopi khat ahi. Hiche hi lhumlam gamgi chu ahi.  
\v 15 Lhanglam gamgi chu Kiriath-jearim khopamma kon'in ahung kipanne. Hiche lhumlam gamchinna konhin ahung kilhungin Naphtoah twinah put namun ahinjotpan,  
\v 16 Ben-Hinnom phaicham pangmol bullah alutnin ahi. Hiche hi Rephaim phaicham sahlang kichaina mun ahi. Hichea konhin Hinnom phaichamma achesuh peh-in Jebus mite chenna lhanglam suh apaltannin En-Rogel chan gei in achonlut peh in ahi.  
\v 17 En-Rogel gamgia kon'in sahlang jotna lammah alutnin En-Shemesh ahinjonin Geliloth (Adummin langa kaltouna toh kigalsai ahitai) chunga alut jellin ahi. Hichea konhin Bohan (Reuben chapa min) songphung geijin achesuh in ahi.  
\v 18 Hichea konhin Jordan phaicham hin galdotna sahlang gamkai langa achepeh in ahi. Hiti chun gamgi chu phaicham lamma achesuh in ahi.  
\v 19 Beth-hoglah sahlang lhang apal galkaijin Chitwi-len sahlang pangah alongin ahi. Hiche hi Jordan vadung lhang langa achaina ahitai. Hiche lhanglang gamgi chu ahitai.  
\v 20 Solam gamgi chu Jordan vadung ahitai. Hiche hi Benjamin phung bahkai ho jouse gamlo dinga kipe gamgi chu ahi.  
\v 21 Hiche ho hi Benjamin phung sunga abahkai ho kipe khopichu ahi. Beth-hoglah, Emek-keziz,  
\v 22 Beth-arabah, Zemaraim, Bethel,  
\v 23 Avvim, Parah, Ophrah,  
\v 24 Kephar-ammoni, Ophni, and Geba— khopi som le ni chule  vella khoho ahiuve  
\v 25 Chujongleh Gibeon, Ramah, Beeroth,  
\v 26 Mizpeh, Kephirah, Mozah,  
\v 27 Rekem, Irpeel, Taralah,  
\v 28 Zela, Haeleph, Jebus (hichu Jerusalem), Gibeah, and Kiriath-jearim — khopi somleli chule  avel'a khoho ahiuve. Hicheng hi Benjamin phungmite le abahkai ho lodia kipe gam ho chu ahi.   
\c 19  
\s1 Simeon Phungmite Gam Kipe  
\p
\v 1 Anichanna’a alodiova gam kipechu Simeon phung sunga phung bahkaiho chu ahiuve.  
\v 2 Simeon gamlo dinga kipe ho chu Beersheba, Sheba, Moladah, \x + \xo 19:2 \xt 1 Thusimbu 4:28-33\x*  
\v 3 Hazar-shual, Belah, Ezem,  
\v 4 Eltolad,Belhul, Hormah,  
\v 5 Ziklag, Bethmarcaboth, Hazar-susah,  
\v 6 Beth-lebaoth chuleh Sharuhon khopi somle thum toh vella khoho puma ahop ahi.  
\v 7 Hichun Ain, Rimmon, Ether, chule Ashan khopi li hotoh akhoneo ho jong ahopme.  
\v 8 Avelluva khohop jouse toh Baalath-beer (Negev ma Ramah jong akitin ahi) chan gei ahi. Hiche ho hi Simeon phungle abahkhai ho gamlo dinga kipea chu ahi.  
\v 9 Amaho kipe gamhi Judah te gamphabep kikah lha a kipe ahi. Ajeh chu Judah gamchu amaho dinga analen valla ahi. Hijeh chun Judah gamsunga kon'in Simeon phungin gamchan phabep aneiyin ahi.   
\s1 Zebulun Mite Gam Kipe  
\p
\v 10 Athum channa gamloding chan kipe chu: Zebulun phung sunga abahkhai ho ahiuve. Zebulun chenna gamgei chu Sarid na ahung kipan ahi.  
\v 11 Hichea konchun lhumlamma achen Maralah ahopan Dabbeesheth akhokhellin Jokneam vadungneo lang ajonnin ahi.  
\v 12 Sarid napat chun agamgihi gamchom jep'a akiheijin, Kishloth-tabor gamgi lang nisolamma nisa hungsodoh nalam ajontai. Chuin Deberath lang ajon kitnin, Japhia langa akilhung touve,  
\v 13 Japhia patchun nisolam ahin lhahin nisa hungsodoh jina Gath-hepher gal Eth-kazin geijin ahung kilhung paiyin chuin Rimmon channin akilhung doh peh in Neah lang jonin ahung kiheikon tai.  
\v 14 Abanin sahlamma agamgi chu Hannathon langa akiheijin Iphtah-el phaiya abeitai.  
\v 15 Khopi ho chu Kattath ahin, Nahalal ahin, Shimron ahin, Idalah ahin, chuleh Bethlehem toh ahi, khopi som le ni toh akhoneo jousetoh ahithai.  
\v 16 Hichenghi Zebulun chate chan agam goulo ahin a insung dungjui uva khopi hicheng toh akhoneo jouse toh chantha ahiuve.   
\s1 Issachar Phung Mite Gam Kipe  
\p
\v 17 Ali channa gamloding chan kipe chu Issachar phung mite le asunga abahkhai ho ahiuve.  
\v 18 Agamgi hopsunga chun Jezreel jong, Kesul’loth jong Shunem jong.  
\v 19 Hapharaim jong Shion jong Anaharath jong,  
\v 20 Rabbith jong Kishion jong Ebez jong,  
\v 21 Remeth, En-gannim jong En-haddah jong, Beth-pazzez jong ahopdoh tai,  
\v 22 Agamgi chun Tabor jong Shahazuman jong chle Beth-shemesh jong ahopan, Jordan vadungah chun agamgi abeitai. Khopi somlegup toh akhoneo jouse toh ahiye.  
\v 23 Hiche hi Issachar chate phung miho goulo achandio ahin, a insung dungjuijin khopi chujat chutoh khoneo chengse toh achantha taove.   
\s1 Asher Phung Mite Gam Kipe  
\p
\v 24 Anga channa gamloding chan kipe chu Asher phung mite le asunga abahkhai ho ahiuve.  
\v 25 Agam chu Helkath jong Hali jong , Beten jong, Achshaph jong,  
\v 26 Allammelech jong, Amad jong chule Mishal jong ahoptai, nilhum lamma Carmel le Shihor-libnath jong ahopsohkeijin,  
\v 27 Chuin agamgi’n nisolam ajotnin, Beth-dagon geijin akilhungin, Zebulun leh Iphtahel phaicham ahopan, sahlam alhah in, Beth-emek leh Neiel geijin akilhung lut in ahi, chujouvin jong agamgi chu Cabul sahlamma achen,  
\v 28 Ebron lam, Rehob lam, Hammon lam, Kanah lam ajonnin, Sidon lengpa geijin akilhung lutne,  
\v 29 Hichun Ramah lamma agamgi chu ahung kihei kitnin Tyre khopi kulpi kikai khumchu ahinpha peh in ahi, chujouvin Hosah lam jonnin akihei kitnin chule Mediterranian twilena atangtai, Mehebel jong Achzib jong,  
\v 30 Ummah jong, Aphek jong chuyle Rehob jong ahin, khopi somnile nitoh akhoneo jouse jong ahi.  
\v 31 Hiche hi a insungu dungjuiya Asher chate phung goulo ahin, khopi hijat leh akhoneo jousetoh ahiye.   
\s1 Naphtali Phung Mite Gam Kipe  
\p
\v 32 Agup channa gamloding chan kipe chu Naphtali phung mite le asunga abahkhai ho ahiuve.  
\v 33 Agamgi chu Heleph a kipat Zaanan-nim apat chule Adami-nekeb apat, Jabneel apat Lakkum chan geijin akilhung lut peh in, chuin Jordan vadunga atangtai.  
\v 34 Chujouvin agamgi chu nilhum lamma akiheijin, Aznoth-tabor lam ajonnin chua kon'in Hukkok lam ajonpai paijin lhanglamma Zebulun ahopan nilhum langa Asher gamgi ahopa kitnin nisolamma Jordan vadung ajuijin ahi.  
\v 35 Kulpi kikaikhum ho chu, Ziddim ahin, Zer ahin, Hammath ahin, Rakkath ahin, Kinnereth ahi.  
\v 36 Adamah ahin, Ramah ahin, Hazor ahin,  
\v 37 Kedesh ahin, Edrei ahin, En-hazor ahin,  
\v 38 Yiron ahin, Migdal-el ahin, Beth-anath ahin, chule Beth-shemesh ahi, khopi somleko toh khoneo chengse toh ahiye.  
\v 39 Ainsung utoh kithuh bepma hichenghi Naphtali chate phung chan agamu ahi, khopi ho hi ahin khoneoho ahin akisim than ahi.   
\s1 Dan Phung Mite Gam Kipe  
\p
\v 40 Asagi channa gamloding chan kipe chu Dan phung mite le asunga abahkhai ho ahiuve.  
\v 41 Chule Dan phung chan agoulo gamchun khopi Zorah jong, Eshtaol jong Ir-shemesh jong,  
\v 42 Shalabbin jong, Aijalon jong, Ithlah jong,  
\v 43 Elon jong Timnath jong, Ekron jong ahin,  
\v 44 Eltekah jong, Gibbethon jong, Baalath jong,  
\v 45 Jehud jong, Bene-berak jong, Gath-rimmon jong,  
\v 46 Chule Me-jarkon le Rakkon toh Joppa to kimai ngat gamsungse sejong ahopsohkeijin ahi.  
\v 47 Dan chaten agamsung achanlou phat uvin akon touvun Leshem khopi agasat uvin, alah jouvun chemjammin asatgam helluvin atoupha uvin asunga acheng tauve, Leshem jong chu apu apau min aputsah uvin Dan asah taove. \x + \xo 19:47 \xt Thutan Vaihom Ho 18:27-29\x*  
\v 48 Hichenghi a insung tohkham bepma Dan chate phunggoul achannu ahin, khopi ho jong khoneo ho jong ahithai.   
\s1 Gam Kipe Nukhah Pen  
\p
\v 49 Gamsung chu abih bih a gouloa chenpha dia akihopsoh helphat uvin, Israel chaten Nun chapa Joshua jong chu alah uva goulo ding gam apeovin ahi.  
\v 50 Pakai thusah in Israel ten Joshua chu athumpen pen khopi Timnath-serah kiti, Ephraim thinglhang gamsunga khopi chu ape taove, amanjong akhopi chu akisah phatnin chennan aneitan ahi.  
\v 51 Eleazer thempupa leh Nun chapa Joshua chule Israel aphungkhai leh a insung dungjui uva alamkai houvin Shiloh munna Pakai angsung laitah’a vang asan’uva anahopdoh peh naogam ahin, hichu Pakai chenna ponbuh kotpi phunga anahopmu ahiye, hiti chun ama hon agamchu ahomsoh tauvin ahi.   
\c 20  
\s1 Hoidohna Thei Khopi Ho  
\p
\v 1 Pakaiyin Joshua kom'a h hiti hin thu ahinseije: \x + \xo 20:1 \xt Minbu 35:9-34; Danbu Ni Na 4:41-43; 19:1-13\x*  
\v 2 “Tun keiman Mose kana seipeh bangin Israel te chun kiselna ding khopiho chu akilhendoh diovin seipehtan  
\v 3 ‘Koitobang hamkhat in mikhattou tupna mong umlouva ahilouleh hettoh louva ahin tha khah tah a ahileh athatpa chunga phulanom athipa sopiho khutna konna ajamlut nading kiselna khopi ho um ding ahi.  
\v 4 Hiche khopiho khatpen’a hi ajamlut teng hiche mithatpahi khopi kelkot phunga upaho masanga achungthu akiphondoh ding, ama hon hiche pa hi khopi sunga alutsah uva amaho kom'a achen theina ding agonpeh diu ahi.  
\v 5 Ijemtia athipa insung mite chu phula dinga ahungu leh lamkai ho chun mithatpa chu amaho kom'a apehlut louding ahi, ajeh chu amapa chun tumasanga kinahna umlou chuleh tupna mong imacha umlouva khutsoiya anatha khah jeh ahi.  
\v 6 Ahinlah mithatpa chu hiche khopia chu umden ding, khopi chun achung thu akhol toh uva athu atandiu ahi, chuleh hiche thilso petna Thempu Chungnung natongpa hinlai sea hiche kom'a chu cheng ding ahi. Hijouteng chuleh ahung jamdohna khopi sung ain munna chu kilekit thei ding ahi.  
\v 7 Hiche ho hi kiselna khopi ho chu: Naphtali thinglhang gam'a din Galilee a um Kadesh, Ephraim thinglhang gam'adin Sechem, Judah thinglhang gam'a din Kiriath-arba (Hebron tina),  
\v 8 Jericho gallang Jordan vadung solama din hiche khopiho hi alhengdoh un ahi: Reuben phung phaicham gammang langa din Bezer; Gad phung mite gamsunga din Gilead na um Ramoth, Manasseh phung mite gamsunga din Bashan’a um Golan ahiuve.  
\v 9 Israel te hihen alah uva cheng gamchom miho hijongleh hiche khopi ho hi kigonpeh a ahiuve. Hiche hi amun khoppi masanga thu kikholna umman louva phulahna a kilhana dinga konna hoidohna aum theina dinga tohgon ahi.   
\c 21  
\s1 Levi Phung Mite Khopi Ho  
\p
\v 1 Hiche jouchun Levi phung sunga lamkaiho chu ahungun Eleazer thempupa toh, Nun chapa Joshua toh chuleh Israel pumpi phung lamkaiho ahung kihoutoh piuvin ahi.  
\v 2 Amaho chu Canaan gam'a Shiloh munna ahungun hiti hin aseijuve, “Keiho hi kaganchateu neh ding hampa phatna gamleh keiho chenna ding khopiho eipehna diuvin Pakaiyin Mose kom'a h anaseijin ahi,” atiuve. \x + \xo 21:2 \xt Minbu 35:1-8\x*  
\v 3 Hiti chun Pakai thupeh dungjuijin Israel mipite chun hiche khopiho le hampa phatna gamho hi amaho gamchan dingin Levi te chu ana piuvin ahi.  
\v 4 Levi phungsunga konna Kohath phung bahkai insung miho Aaron chilhah ho chu atil abulla Judah, Simeon leh Benjamin phungho ana kipe khopi somlethum ho chu ape tauvin ahi.  
\v 5 Tumasang Ephraim, Dan leh Manasseh phung akehkhat anakipesa khopi somkhat chu Kohath phungkhai insungmi dang ho chu anapeovin ahi.  
\v 6 Tumasang’a Issachar, Asher, Naphtali chuleh Manasseh phungkeh khat ana kipesa khopi somle thumchu Gershon phung bahkhai ho chu anapeuvin ahi.  
\v 7 Tumasang’a Reuben, Gad leh Zebulun phungho ana kipesa khopi som le ni ho chu Merari phungkhai ho chu anapeovin ahi.  
\v 8 Pakaiyin Mose anathupeh dungjuijin Israel chaten khopi hichengse hileh hamhing phatna gam hichenghi vangkisanpeh bang banga Levi te anapeh u ahiye.  
\v 9 Judah leh Simeon phunga kon'in Israel chaten khopi hichengsehi anape taove.  
\v 10 Akhopi chengsehi Aaron chilhah ho Kohath chate insung leh Levi miho mama insungkhat ching taovein ahi, ajeh chu vangkisan chu amaho dia hung pha masa ahi.  
\v 11 Israel chaten amaho chu Kiriath-arba kiti, hichea Arba hi Anak pa ahin, akhopi Hebron jong kiti, Juda thinglhang gam'a khopi le akimvella hamhing gamchengse chu apetaove.  
\v 12 Khopi loujao chengsele akhoneoho vang chu Jephunneh chapa Caleb chenna dinga kipesa ahitai.  
\v 13 Aaron thempupa chilhah te chu Israel chaten mithatho kiselna khopi Hebron le ahamhing gamsung jouse apeovin, Libnah le ahamhing gam pumpi jong anapeuve.  
\v 14 Jattir khopile Eshtemoa ahamhing gamjong apeovin ahi.  
\v 15 Holonle ahamhing gamjouse apeovin, Debirle hamhing gamjong apeh thaovin ahi.  
\v 16 Chule Ain khopile ahamhing gamsung apehthaovin Juttah le ahamhing gamjong apeove. Beth-shemesh le ahamhing apeh tauvin, hiti chun hiche phungni sunga kon hin khopi ko apedoh taove.  
\v 17 Benjamin phunga kon'in Gibeon khopile ahamhing gamjong apeovin, Giba le ahamhing gamjong apeovin,  
\v 18 Anathoth khopile ahamhing gamsungsese toh apummin Almon khopile ahamhing gamsungse jong apeovin ahi.  
\v 19 Aaron thempupa chilhah achate chan khopi chengsechu abonchan khopi somlethum toh ahamhing gamsungse toh ahopthan ahi.  
\v 20 Levi mite lah a Kohath insungmi, Kohath chate amoh chengse chu Ephraim phunga konna achandio khopi akihoppeh tai.  
\v 21 Hiche Kohath chate amoh chengse chu mithatho kiselna ding khopi Shechem le ahamhing gamsunga, Ephraim thinglhang gamsung chu apeovin, Gezer khopile ahamhing gamsung jong apeovin ahi.  
\v 22 Kibzaim khopi le ahamhing gamjong apeove, khopi li alhingin ahi.  
\v 23 Chule Dan phunga kon'in Eltekeh khopile ahamhing gam apeovin Gibbethon khopi le ahamhing gam apeove;  
\v 24 Aijalon khopile ahamhing gamjong apeove, khopi li ma alhing in ahi.  
\v 25 Manasseh phunga kon'in jong Taanach khopile ahamhing gam apeovin Gath-rimmon khopile ahamhing gam apeove; hichu khopi ni ahi.  
\v 26 Kohath chate amoh chengse insung mite chan khopichu abonchan khopi somkhat le ahamhing gamjouse toh ahopthai.  
\v 27 Levi te inko lah a a insung khat Gershon chate jongchu Manasseh phungkah khat a kon'in asandiu chu apeovin, Bashan gamsungse Golan khopile ahamhing gamsungse apeove; hiche khopi jong mithat ho kiselna khopi mama ahi, chule Be-eshterah khopi le ahamhing gamsung jong ahin, khopi ni hi apeovin ahi.  
\v 28 Chujongleh Issachar phunga kon'in jong Kishion khopi le ahamhing gamsung apeovin, Daberath khopile ahamhing gamsung sese jong apeove.  
\v 29 Chule Jarmuth khopi le ahamhing gamsung apeovin, En-ganmin khopile ahamhing gamsung jong apeh thaovin ahile, khopili alhing in ahi.  
\v 30 Asher phunga kon'in jong Mishal leh Abdon khopi le ahamhing gamjong apeove,  
\v 31 Helkath khopi le ahanhing gamsung jong apeovin chule Rehob khopile ahamhing gamjong apeovin ahileh khopi li ma alhingtai.  
\v 32 Naphtali phung sunga kon'in jong Galilee gamsunga Kedesh le ahamhing gamsung jong apeovin, hiche khopi jonghi mithat ho kiselna khopi ma ahi, Hammoth-dor le ahamhing gamsung jong apeovin, chule kartan khopi le ahamhing gamsung jong apeh thaovin, abonnin khopi thum alhingtai.  
\v 33 Gershon chate inko chujat dinga khopi kipedoh chengse chu abonchan khopi somle thum alhingin ahamhing gamsung sesetoh ahi tha cheh in ahi.  
\v 34 Levi te mi amoh chengse, Merari chate chu Zubulun phunga kon'in achandio akipen, Jok-neam khopi le ahamhing gamsung apeovin, Kartah khopi le ahamhing gamsung apeove.  
\v 35 Dimnah khopile ahamhing gamsungse apeovin, Nahalal khopile ahamhing gamsung jong apeove, abonnin khopi li alhingin ahi.  
\v 36 Reuben phunga kon'in jong Bezer khopile ahamhing gamsung chu apeovin, Jahaz khopile ahamhing gamsungse sejong apeove.  
\v 37 Kedemoth khopile ahamhing gamsungse apeovin chule Mephaath khopi le ahamhing gamsungse sejong apeovin ahileh khopi li alhinge.  
\v 38 Gad phunga kon'in jong Gilead gamsunga Ramoth khopi le ahamhing gamsungse se apeovin, hiche khopi jonghi mithat ho kiselna khopi mama ahiye; Mahanaim khopile ahamhing gamsung jong apeovin,  
\v 39 Heshbon khopile ahamhing gamsungse sejong apeovin, Jazer khopi le ahamhing gamsungse se apeovin ahileh abonnin khopi li alhingin ahi.  
\v 40 Merari chate inko chujatpi Levi inkote lah a aum nalaiho dia kipedoh khopi chengse abonchan khopi som le ni alhingin ahi.  
\v 41 Israel chate lah a Levi te khopi chengse chu abonnin khopi somlileget alhingin, ahamhing gamsungse setoh ahitha cheh in ahi.  
\v 42 Khopi hijatchun akimvel khopam dunga hamhing gam aneicheh uvin, hitobanga hi khopi chujat chu changsoh hel ahiuve.   
\s1 Israel ten Canaan Gam Alo-U  
\p
\v 43 Hitobang hin apu apateu henga akihahselna bang bangin Pakaiyin Canaan gam pumpi chu Israel te apetai; Israel tenjong agam pumpi chu atoupha uvin achengtaove.  
\v 44 Chujongleh apu apateu henga akihahselna bangchun Pakaiyin Israel te chu ajet avei’a mitea kon'in akicholdo sahtai; agalteu khatna khat jengcha jong amaho ting tan jouvah abeihel tan ahi; ijeh nem itileh Pakaiyin agalteu abonchan akhut uva apedoh tan ahi.  
\v 45 Pakaiyin Israel te insung dinga akitepna pha chengse chu khatcha alhinglel abei hellin, abonchan athutep chengse agui lhung sohkeiyin ahi.   
\c 22  
\s1 Solam A Cheng Phungho Hung Kile  
\p
\v 1 Joshua Reuben chate le Gad chate chule Manasseh phungkeh khat chutoh akoukhommin,  
\v 2 Ajah uva hiti hin aseitai, “Nanghon Pakai lhacha Mose in nathupeh jouse abonchan nanitsohkeiyun, keiman nango ka seipeh ka thusei jouse jong nangai taove, \x + \xo 22:2 \xt Minbu 32:20-32; Joshua 1:12-15\x*  
\v 3 Nikho hijat sunghin tuni geijin nang hon nasopi phungdang te ho jong nadalha dehpouvin, Pakai na Pathenn uvin nathupeh chnegseu jong chingthei tah in nanit sohkei’un ahi.  
\v 4 Tunvang Pakai na Pathen uvin athutep bang bangin nasopi phungdang te ho jong jong akitepna bangin akicholdosah tai, hijeh chun tun kiheijun lang Jordan gal lamma Pakai lhacha Mose’n napeh naugam, nangho chenna gamsung nagoulo’u, na inlammu jonnin chetauvin,  
\v 5 Pakai lhacha Mose’n nathupeh u danthupeh chengse chu nanit jingna diuvin ching theiyun, Pakai na Pathen'u nangailut nuva ama lamlhah jouse najuithem uva athupeh chengse nanit’uva ama jong nakolchah jing uva, chule nalungthim pumpiu le nahinkho pumpiuva amakin jeng naboldiu nagin jing diu ahi.” ati.  
\v 6 Hiti chun Joshua’n amaho chu phatthei aboh in, phatthei abohjou phatnin asoldohtai, amaho jong ainlam cheh uva achetaove.  
\v 7 Manasseh phung akehkhat chu Bashan gamsunga Mose’n achandiu gam anapehsa ahin, Manasseh phungkeh khatma chu Joshua’n Jordan vadung gal nilhumlam, asopi teu dang ho lah a chenmun anapeh ahiye. Amaho chu Joshua’n ainlammuva asoldoh phatnin abonchauvin phatthei abohsohkeijin ahi;  
\v 8 Ajah uva Joshua’n hitin ati, “Neilegou tampitah kipoh uvin lang gancha jong tamtah kipoh uvin lang naponbuh skonna muncheh a kile tauvin, nagal mite uva konna nachomdoh jouseu jong kihommun” ati.  
\v 9 Hijeh chun Reuben chate le Gad chate chuleh Manasseh phung kehkhat chun Israel chate amoh chengse chu Canaan gam'a Shiloh kiti khopiah chun adalhauvin, amaho chu Pakaiyin Mose athupeh banga agamlosa sung’u Gilead gamsung jonnin ache taove.   
\s1 Solam’a Cheng Hon Pathen Maicham Atundoh-U  
\p
\v 10 Ahin amaho chu Canaan sung’a aum jinglai un, Geliloth kiti mun Jordan vadung kom'a h chun, Reuben chate le Gad chate chule Manasseh phung kehkhat chu akinga pa un, maicham phung lentah le thupitah khat asemmun ahi.  
\v 11 Israel chaten, Reuben chate le Gad chate, chule Manasseh phung kehkhat chun Canaan gam mongchin Jordan vapang lhangchung khat’a Israel chate gamsunga khun maicham asemmu chu ajahdoh taove.  
\v 12 Athudol hi Israel chaten ajahdoh phatnun Shiloh munna cheng Israel chate khopi pumpi akikhommuvin amaho chu galla sat thodin agotaove.  
\v 13 Ahinlah, amasan, Eleazar thempu chapa Phinehas lamkainan mi phabep Reuben phung mite le Gad chule Manasseh phung keh khat toh kihoudin anasol uve.  
\v 14 Hichea kihoulimpi dia kalsong miho chu Israel phunglah a lamkai som ahiuvin, a insungkhat bahkailhah’a aluboh cheh, chule Israel insung phung khat cheh a konna kilhengdoh phung upacheh mi ahiuve.  
\v 15 Amaho chu Gilead gam ahunglhun phat un, Reuben chate le Gad chate chule Manasseh phung kehkhat hengah hitin aseijuve,  
\v 16 Pakai khoppi amiten hitin aseijun, “Ipi dinga nang hon tulaija hi Israel Pathen douna thil nabolluva Pakai nung najuidauva nakiheimang jeng uva nacham chamma maicham nakisem jeng uva Pakai douna hitobang pihi nabollu hitam? \x + \xo 22:16 \xt Danbu Ni Na 12:13,14\x*  
\v 17 Peor munna ichonset nau jong phaset nasah louvu ham? Hichea konna bon ithensoh jou loulaiju hilouham? Hiche ichonset jeh uva jong chu Pakai khoppi mipi chunga jong gamna hise ana langsa ahi, \x + \xo 22:17 \xt Minbu 25:1-9\x*  
\v 18 Tuni geija jong nangho hitobanga hi Pakai chu iti nadalhah uva nakihei mang jengdiu hitam? Tuni jenga jong nang hon Pakai doumah nabolluva ahileh ama chu Israel khoppi pumpi chung jenga jong hung lunghang jengding ahi.  
\v 19 Nachennao gamsung athenlouva ahijongleh hung galkai junlang Pakai Houbuh kiskonna gamsung Pakai gamsunga khun keiho lah a hung cheng jenguvin, Pakai doumah hi nabol louhel diu, Pakai I-Pathen'u maicham semna tailouva nacham nachamma nakisem thu-uva keiho geija doumah hol neiso louhel dingu ahi.  
\v 20 Suhmang dinga kikatdohsa thil-ho chunga Achan kitipa Zerah chapan tohkhel aneiyu chu Israel khoppi pumpi chunga lunghanna hungchu jengsa hilouham?” ahung tiuve. \x + \xo 22:20 \xt Joshua 7:1-26\x*  
\v 21 Reuben chate le Gad chate chule Manasseh phung kehkhat chun Israel phungsunga insungmi upaho donbutnan aneiyun,  
\v 22 “Pakai, Hatchungnung chu Pathen ahi! Pakai, Hatchungnung chu Pathen ahi! Aman thudih le thutah chu ahenai, chule Israel chaten jong nahet uva pha ahi. Keihon maicham kasemmu hi Pakai doumah nadia kabollu ahipoi. Kathilbol uhi doumah lam ahitah a Pakai dinga tahsan suhbeina ahi ding leh keiho hi tunin eighing hoida jenguvin,  
\v 23 Ahin maicham khat kasemdoh jeh uva Pakai nungjuija konna kihei mang’na ahi mongding leh ahilouva keihon hiche maicham chunga hi pumgo thil hihenlang lhosoh thilto hijongleh chamna thilto hijongleh kato’uva ahivang leh Pakaiyin kachung uva gotna eipe jeng uhen.  
\v 24 Tahbeh mong in, keihon hiche maicham kasem uhi katijat man uva kabollu ahi bouve, ajeh chu khonung tengleh nachateuvin kachateu jah a, ‘Nanghon Pakai Israel Pathen chu koi thusah na nahou uham?’ ahin ti diu ahi  
\v 25 Ajeh chu Pakaiyin nanghotoh Reuben chate Gad chate, ikikah uva Jordan vadung hi gamgia asemsa ahitai, khunungleh nangho Pakaiya chan nanei pouve ati theiju ahi, hitobanga hi nachateuvin kachateu hi Pakai ahousahda theiyu ahi.  
\v 26 Hiche jeh a chu keihon ka maicham semmu hi pumgo thilto gonading le kilhaina gantha nading ahipoi,  
\v 27 Ahin keiho leh nangho kikah a hetjingna dia kasemmu ahi, chujongleh hichun eiho nunga khangthahte kah a jong hettohsahnan hungpangin tin, keihon jong Pakai angsunga ama kin kabol mong mong uvin pumgo thilto jong kilhaina gantha jong chule chamna thilto gantha jong kabol naove ti hetjing’nan in hung pang nante, katiu ahi, achuti louva ahileh khonung phatleh nachateuvin keiho chate jah a, “Nanghon Pakaiya chan nanei pouve” ahinti khah teidiu ahi tia kabollu ahi bouve.  
\v 28 Ijemtia hita chu ahinsei khah tah ujongleh, khonung a katu kachateu vin jong, ‘Veuvin, Pakai dinga kapu kapateuvin asemsa maicham khu pumgo thilto kitona jong hilou, kilhaina ganthana maicham jong hilou, ahin nangho leh keihon Pakaiyah chan inanei khommui ti melchih’nan pang nante’ katiu ahi bouve.  
\v 29 Itihchan hijongleh keihon Pakai doumah kabol louhel diu ahin, chujongleh Pakai i-Pathen'u maicham amaHoubuh maiya kitung tailouva keihon kacham chamuva pumgo thilto tona ding leh lhosoh thilto tonading chule kilhaina ganthana dia maicham kasemmuva Pakai nunga konna kaki heimang louhel diu ahi” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 30 Reuben chate leh Gad chate chule Manasseh phung kehkhat thusei ho jouse chu ajah doh phat uvin, Phinehas thempupa le akilhonpi khoppi lamkai ho leh Israel insung jouse phung upa chengsen chu alungu alhaisel tauvin ahi.  
\v 31 Eleazer thempupa chapa Phinehas chun Reuben chate Gad chate chule Manasseh phung kehkhat jah a aseipeh in, “I-lah uva Pakai ching jingnai, ti keihon tunin kahe taove, ijeh-inem itileh keihon nangho kanaginmo bang’un Pakai dounan thilse ima nabol hih naove chuleh nang hon Pakai khutna kon'in jong Israel chate hi suhmang’a aum thei naova kon'in nahuhdoh taove” atin ahi.  
\v 32 Chujouvin Eleazer thempupa chapa Phinehas le lamkaiho chun Reuben chate le Gad chate Gilead gamsung’a chun adalhauvin, hikom'a kon chun Canaan gamlam, Israel chate chenna lamma ahung kile tauvin, Israel te henga chun thilsoh umchan thu chengse chu lhut tauvin ahi.  
\v 33 Athulhutnu chun Israel chate chu alungdamsah lheh jengin ahi, chuphatnin Israel chaten jong Pathen chate avahchoijun, Reuben chate le Gad chate chenna gamsung suhmang ding le galbol ding jong aseipoh kit tapouve.  
\v 34 Reuben chate le Gad chaten maicham asemsau chu ‘Hettohsah’ tin aminsah tauvin ahi, ama hon aseijun, “Ijeh-inem ititle eiho le amaho kikah a Pakai chu eiho Pathen jong ahi ti hettohsah a pang ahi,” atiuve.   
\c 23  
\s1 Joshua’n Lhahna Thu Asei  
\p
\v 1 Kum phabep ache nungin Pakaiyin Israel mipite hi agal mihouva kon'in akicholdo sahtan ahi. Joshua jong ateh lheh tan,  
\v 2 Aman Israel te upaho leh lamkaiho thutan ho leh vaihom ho akoukhommin, aman amaho kom'a hiti hin asije, “Tuhin keima kateh lhehtai,  
\v 3 Pakai Pathen'in keima phat sunga hi itobang thil nabolpeh uham ti nang hon namusohkeijun ahi. Pakai naPathen'in namelma teu gal nasat peh un ahi.  
\v 4 Keiman imelma teu gam ilahsah houleh ihinlah ding hou nachen nao gam dingin kahin hoppeh taove agamsunghi Jordan vadunga pat na Mediterranean twikhanglen lhumlam gei ahi.  
\v 5 Tun hiche hi nangho gam hi ding ahitai, ajeh chu na Pakai na Pathen'u ama tah in agamsung miho abkonna nadeldoh pehdingu ahi. Nanghon agammuhi Pakai na Pathen'un nateppeh bang uva nalodiu ahitai.  
\v 6 Hijeh chun Mose’n danbua anajihlut banga ichepi theina diuvin chingthei jep uhitin, hitia chu kijethei hihen lang kiveihei hijongleh ichekhel louna diuvin chingthei uhite.  
\v 7 Hijeh chun hiche gamsunga um nalaiho lah a ilhah manglou nadiuvin dingdet uhite. Amaho semthu pathenho nahouthei loudiu le akinna jong nakimanchah loudiu, kihahselna a jong naman theiloudiu amin na amin ujong naphah poh theilou diu ahi.  
\v 8 Amavang na Pakai na Pathen chu tunigeija dettah a nahin kolchah bang uva hi nakolchah jing ding ahi.  
\v 9 Ajeh chu Pakaiyin nam hattah tahho nahin deldoh pehun koima chan nangho hi alonaje nahi pouvin ahi.  
\v 10 Nangho mikhat seh injong misangkhat nadeljam theidiu ahi, ajeh chu Pakai na Pathen'un akitepna bangin nagal’u nasatpeh tauvin ahi. \x + \xo 23:10 \xt Danbu Ni Na 32:30; \xt Danbu Ni Na 3:22\x*  
\v 11 Hijeh chun na Pakai na Pathen'u nangailut jing nadiuvin, chingtheijun,  
\v 12 “Amavang nangho ama a konna nakihei manguva nalahuva nanghotoh umkhom namdang ho chondan nalahuva amahotoh nakichento uva ahileh,  
\v 13 Hiteng chuleh nakihet diu chu Pakai na Pathen'un amaho chu nanodoh pehloudiu ahitai. Hititah sanga chu amaho joh hi nakipal nadiuva nalhemlhauva hungpang diu, namit uva lingle khaova hungpang diu chuleh akhkonna le Pakai na Pathen'un napehnao gamphalaija konna delmanga nahung umdiu ahi.  
\v 14 “Vannoi leiset chena dolla keimahi kahung thivah ding ahitai. Pakai na Pathen'un akitepna jouse nasuhbukip tauvin khatcha jong athkonna aumpoi tihi nalungthimmu giltah in naheuve.  
\v 15 Ahinlah Pakai na Pathen'un akitepna banga thilpha jouse napeh bang’uva hi, athu na ngailou uleh nachung uva hahsatna ahin lhunkhum sahdiu ahi. Aman gampha napeh naova konna hi na suhmang diu ahi.  
\v 16 Nanghon Pakai na Pathen'u kitepna hi nanit lou uva semthu pathen ho nahin hou uva akin nahin bolluva ahileh nangho douna-a a lunghanna mei hung koujah jengding chutenglehchun aman napehnao gampha tah a konna hi namahthah diu ahi.   
\c 24  
\s1 Pathen Toh Kitepna Kithah Sem  
\p
\v 1 Hiche jouchun Joshua’n Israel phung jousechu upaho leh lamkai ho chule thutan vaihom ho jouse Shechem mah anakou khommin hiti chun amaho ahungun Pathen angsung'ah ahung dingun ahi.  
\v 2 Joshua’n mipi abonchao jeh a chun hitin anaseije, “Pakai Israel Pathen'in hitin aseije, napului teniu Abraham le Nahor pa Terah chu khanglui laijin Euphrates lui galla achenguvin chujongleh ama hon pathen limsemthu ho jong ana houvun ahi. \x + \xo 24:2 \xt Semtilbu 11:27\x*  
\v 3 Ahinla Keiman napuluiju Abraham chu Euphrate gallam akon chun Canaan gam'a kahin puilutnin ahi. Keiman achapa Isaac’a kon'in chilhah tamtah kanapen ahi. \x + \xo 24:3 \xt Semtilbu 12:1-9; \xt Semtilbu 21:1-3\x*  
\v 4 Isaac chu Jacob le Esau kanapen ahi. Esau chu Seir molsang langchu kanapen, Jacob le achilhah te chu Egypt langa anache suh un ahi. \x + \xo 24:4 \xt Semtilbu 25:24-26; \xt Semtilbu 36:8; Danbu Ni Na 2:5; \xt Semtilbu 46:1-7\x*  
\v 5 Hiche jouchun Keiman Mose le Aaron kanasollin chuleh Egypt machun natset khohtah kana laansah in, hiche jouchun Keiman nangho chu chamlhat mite nahitheina diuvin kahin puidoh un ahi. \x + \xo 24:5 \xt Potdohbu 3:1—12:42\x*  
\v 6 Ahinlah napu napa teuhin twikhanglensan alhunphatnun, Egypt miten Sakol kangtalai jin nahin nungdel tauvin ahi. \x + \xo 24:6 \xt Potdohbu 14:1-31\x*  
\v 7 Hichun napu napa teuchu Pakai kom'a ahung penjah jeng phat nun nangho leh Egypt te kikah a thim kana jinsah in, twikhanglen chu kana vallhun sahin, hiti chun namitmu changtah un Egypt te chunga hitobanghi kana tongdoh in ahi. HIche jouchun gamthip noijah phatsottah nahung chengtauvin ahi.  
\v 8 Ajona in Keiman nangho chu Jordan pang nisolamma cheng Amor mite gamsunga kahin puilut’un ahi. Ama hon nangho chu nakisat piuvin ahinlah keiman amaho chu namasangtah uva ka suhmang pehun ahi. Keiman amaho chunga galjona kapeuvin hiti chun nang hon agamsungu nalo uvin nachen khum tauvin ahi. \x + \xo 24:8 \xt Minbu 21:21-35\x*  
\v 9 Hiche jouchun Moab lengpa Zippor chapa Balak chun Israel dounan gal ahin boltauvin ahi. Aman Be’or chapa Balaam chu nangho gaosap dingin ahin kouvin \x + \xo 24:9 \xt Minbu 22:1—24:25\x*  
\v 10 Ahinlah keiman kana noppeh pon, keiman Balaam chu nangho joh phatthei kanaboh sahtan, hiti chun nangho chu Balak a kon'in kana huhdoh tan ahi.  
\v 11 Nangho Jordan vadung nagalkai juva Jericho nahung lhun phatnun, Amor mite, Perizz mite, Canaan mite, Hit mite, Girgash mite, Hivi mite le Jebus miten bang bangun Jericho mitenjong nanadou tauvin ahi. Ahinlah keiman amaho chu kana josah tauvin ahi. \x + \xo 24:11 \xt Joshua 3:14-17; \xt Joshua 6:1-21\x*  
\v 12 Keiman Amor lengteni delmang dingin nangho masang’ah khoise kanasol masan ahi. Nagaljonao chu nachem muleh nathalpi ahipon ahi. \x + \xo 24:12 \xt Potdohbu 23:28; Danbu Ni Na 7:20\x*  
\v 13 Nathanat nao hilou gamchu kapeuvin chuleh nasah dohsao hilou khopiho kapeuvin nang hon tun nachenpha tauvin ahi. Natusao hilou leh Olive gammang jong naneh diuvin kapeuvin ahi. \x + \xo 24:13 \xt Danbu Ni Na 6:10,11\x*  
\v 14 “Hijeh chun nalungthim pumpiuvin Pakai chu gingunlang akin bolluvin. Napu napateuvin Euphrate vadung gallang Egypt ma anachenlai uva ana houvu semthu pathen ho chu a itih a dingin paimang soh helluvin lang Pakai kin jengbou bollun.  
\v 15 Ahinlah hiche Pakai kin hi nabol nom louhel uva ahileh koikin nabol dinguham tuni hin kilhen khen jenguvin. Euphrates gallanga napu napateu semthu pathen ho chu nahou joh diuham? Ahilouleh tua nachennao gamsunga ana chengah Amor mite semthu pathen hojoh chu nahou diuham kilhen khen tauvin. Keima leh ka insung miten vang a i-tihchan hijongleh Pakai kinchu kabol jing jeng dingu ahi,” ati.  
\v 16 Mipiten hiti hin adonbut nuva, “Keihon itih hijongleh Pakai chu nungsunna semthu pathen dang kin kabollouhel diu ahi.  
\v 17 Ajeh chu Pakai Pathen le keiho leh kapu kapateu Egypt gam sohchan na a konna eina huhdoh uva chu ahi. Aman datmo umthil kidang nasatah keiho mitmulah in ana bollin ahi. Keihon gamthipnoi melmate lah a lam kahin jotnaova hin aman eihin pui galkai uvah ama bou ahi.  
\v 18 Hiche gam'a anacheng Amor miteleh namdang ho jouse eina nodoh peh uvah Pakai ama bou ahi. Hijeh chun keihon jong ama kinbou kaboldiu ahi, ajeh chu ama bou hi ka Pathen'u ahi”.  
\v 19 Hichun Joshua in mipi ho chu agihsallin in hitin aseije, “Nanghon Pakai kinhi boljou pouvin nate, ajeh chu Pakai hi thengtah leh thangthip Pathen ahi. Aman na chonset nau leh Ama nadou ah o jouse nangaidam pouvinte.  
\v 20 Ahin nang hon Pakai chu nanungsun uva semthu pathen dang kin nahin boljeng tah uva ahileh tumasangin nahin ngailulheh jengu jonglehng, nangho douva hung pangding nahin suhmang dingu ahi” ati.  
\v 21 Ahinlah mipi ho chun Joshua chu adonbut un, “Ahipoi keihon Pakai kinchu kabol teidiu ahi” atiuve.  
\v 22 Joshua’n jong aseijin, “Nangho nathulhuhnao chunga nanh ho leh nangho a hettohsah nahiuve, nang hon Pakai kin bolding nakilhen taove” ati. Ama hon adonbutnun, “Henge, keihon ka thusei juhi keiho mama ahetoh kahiuve,” atiuvin ahi.  
\v 23 Joshua’n aseijin, “Aphai hute ahileh nalah uva milimsemthu ho chu sumang unlang Pakai na Pathen'u langa chun kiheijun lang nalungthim pumpi peuvin,” ati.  
\v 24 Mipite chun Joshua kom'a asejun, “Keihon, Pakai Pathen kinjong kaboldiu, ama thujengbou kangai diu ahi” atiuve.  
\v 25 Hiti chun Joshua’n hiche nikho chun Shechem’ah mipi chutoh kitep nakhat ana sem’un Pakai thupeh ho leh adanthupeh ho chu anit diuvin ana kitepsah in ahi.  
\v 26 Joshua’n hiche ho chu Pathen dan lekhabua anajihlut nin ahi. Chuleh hiche  
\p hetjingna dinga hin songlentah khat Pakai  
\p ponbun kom gangpi phungnoi ana tungdoh in ahi.   
\p
\v 27 Joshua’n mipi ho kom'a h anaseije, “Pakaiyin eiho kom'a aseijouse chu hiche song hin ajasohkeijin ahi. Nangho Pakaiya nakitep naova konna nanung chonnuva ahileh hiche hi nangho douna-a hettohsah hi ding ahi” ati.  
\v 28 Hiche jouchun, Joshua’n mipi ho chu abonchan ainlam cheh a asoldohtan ahi.   
\s1 Gamtep Gam’a Kivui Lamkai Ho  
\p
\v 29 Hiche jouhin Pakai lhacha Nun chapa Joshua chu kum jakhat le somkhat alhinchun athitan ahi.  
\v 30 ama hon ama gamchan dinga ana kipehna mun, Gaash mol sahlang Ephraim thinglhang gam Timnath-serah munnah anavui tauvin ahi. \x + \xo 24:30 \xt Joshua 19:49,50\x*  
\v 31 Israel mipite chun, Joshua hinlaisen, chuleh Pakaiyin Israel tedinga anabol hojouse atahsa tah a hin hechen Joshua  
\p thinunga hingnalai upaho hinlai sungsen Pakai kin phatah in ahin bollun ahi.   
\p
\v 32 Israel ten Egypt ahin dalhah uva ahinpoh u Joseph gu-ho chu, Jacob min Hamor chatea konna dangka jakhatna anachoh gamsung Shechem munna chun anavuijun ahi. Hiche gamhi Joseph chilhahho chan dinga anakipe gamsunga chu umma ahi. \x + \xo 24:32 \xt Semtilbu 33:19; 50:24,25; Potdohbu 13:19; Jn 4:5; Act 7:16\x*  
\v 33 Aaron chapa Eleazer athitai. Ama chu achapa Phinehas anakipe Gibeah khopi sung Ephraim thinglhangah anavuijun ahi.   